20reach%20the%20numerical%20allocations%2C%20the%20US%20federal%20immigration%20agency%20has%20announced%2C%20a%20decision%20that%20could%20benefit%20more%20Indian%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Citizenship%20and%20Immigration%20Services%20(USCIS)%20said%20on%20Thursday%20that%20it%20will%20select%20the%20additional%20registrations%20from%20the%20previously%20submitted%20electronic%20registrations%20using%20a%20random%20selection%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%2C%20the%20USCIS%20conducted%20an%20initial%20random%20selection%20of%20properly%20submitted%20electronic%20registrations%20for%20the%20fiscal%20year%20(FY)%202024%20H-1B%20cap%2C%20including%20for%20beneficiaries%20eligible%20for%20the%20advanced%20degree%20exemption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnly%20those%20petitioners%20with%20selected%20registrations%20for%20FY%202024%20are%20eligible%20to%20file%20H-1B%20cap-subject%20petitions.%20The%20initial%20filing%20period%20for%20those%20with%20selected%20registrations%20for%20FY%202024%20was%20from%20April%201%2C%202023%2C%20through%20June%2030%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20H-1B%20visa%20is%20a%20non-immigrant%20visa%20that%20allows%20US%20companies%20to%20employ%20foreign%20workers%20in%20speciality%20occupations%20that%20require%20theoretical%20or%20technical%20expertise.%20Technology%20companies%20depend%20on%20it%20to%20hire%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20employees%20each%20year%20from%20countries%20like%20India%20and%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20recently%20determined%20that%20we%20would%20need%20to%20select%20additional%20registrations%20to%20reach%20the%20FY%202024%20numerical%20allocations.%20Soon%2C%20we%20will%20select%20additional%20registrations%20from%20previously%20submitted%20electronic%20registrations%20using%20a%20random%20selection%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20USCIS%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20will%20announce%20once%20we%20have%20completed%20this%20second%20selection%20process%20and%20have%20notified%20all%20prospective%20petitioners%20with%20selected%20registrations%20from%20this%20round%20of%20selection%20that%20they%20are%20eligible%20to%20file%20an%20H-1B%20cap-subject%20petition%20for%20the%20beneficiary%20named%20in%20the%20applicable%20selected%20registration%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20with%20selected%20registrations%20will%20have%20their%20accounts%20updated%20to%20include%20a%20selection%20notice%2C%20which%20includes%20details%20of%20when%20and%20where%20to%20file%2C%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20mandated%20by%20Congress%2C%20USCIS%20can%20issue%20a%20maximum%20of%2065%2C000%20H-1B%20visas%20in%20a%20year.%20It%20can%20also%20issue%20another%2020%2C000%20H-1B%20visas%20to%20foreign%20students%20who%20have%20completed%20higher%20studies%20from%20a%20US%20university%20in%20Science%2C%20Technology%2C%20Engineering%20and%20Mathematics%20(STEM)%20subjects.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690529340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2018-01%2Fstatue-of-liberty_650x400_61516584069.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fh-1b-visa-2nd-lottery-round-to-be-held-this-year-says-us-immigration-office-4247797%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20second%20round%20of%20random%20lottery%20selection%20for%20the%20much%20sought-after%20H-1B%20visas%20for%20fiscal%202024%20will%20soon%20begin%20after%20it%20was%20determined%20that%20%26quot%3Badditional%20registrations%26quot%3B%20need%20to%20be%20selected%20to%20reach%20the%20numerical%20allocations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fh-1b-visa-2nd-lottery-round-to-be-held-this-year-says-us-immigration-office-4247797%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fh-1b-visa-2nd-lottery-round-to-be-held-this-year-says-us-immigration-office-4247797%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findians-abroad%2Fh-1b-visa-2nd-lottery-round-to-be-held-this-year-says-us-immigration-office-4247797%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Please%20Help%20Me%5C%22%3A%20Distraught%20Byju's%20Employee%20Breaks%20Down%20In%20Tears%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThere%20seems%20to%20be%20no%20end%20in%20sight%20for%20the%20troubles%20EdTech%20company%20Byju's%20is%20facing.%20From%20raids%20to%20massive%20layoffs%2C%20this%20once%20high-flying%20tutoring%20start-up%20has%20been%20in%20crisis%20mode%20for%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20an%20employee%20of%20Byju's%2C%20marked%20for%20layoff%2C%20has%20shared%20her%20experience%20with%20the%20company%20in%20a%20tearful%20video%20posted%20on%20LinkedIn.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20she%20is%20seen%20asking%20for%20help%20from%20the%20government%20and%20blaming%20the%20company%20for%20committing%20fraud%20against%20employees%20and%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fposts%2Fakansha-khemka-4384b7226_byjus-byjuraveendran-divyagokulnath-activity-7090213821776064513-NDWG%5C%22%3EAkansha%20Khemka%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20working%20as%20an%20Academic%20Specialist%20at%20Byju's%20for%20the%20last%20one%20and%20a%20half%20years%2C%20said%20she%20is%20the%20sole%20breadwinner%20of%20the%20house%2C%20and%20Byju's%20has%20not%20released%20all%20her%20dues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20haven't%20paid%20my%20variables%20and%20the%20encashment%20of%20my%20earned%20leaves.%20They%20sent%20me%20a%20letter%20asking%20me%20to%20resign%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20the%20only%20earning%20member%20in%20the%20family%2C%20my%20husband%20is%20unwell%20and%20I%20have%20loans%20to%20repay.%20How%20will%20I%20survive%20if%20they%20don't%20release%20my%20salary%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20tearful%20Akansha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20request%20that%20our%20government%20please%20help%20me%20and%20other%20employees%20escape%20this%20toxic%20work%20culture.%20Byju's%20is%20committing%20fraud%20from%20all%20sides%2C%20including%20employees%20and%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20wrote%20in%20the%20caption.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20comes%20two%20days%20after%20news%20of%20Byju's%20founder%20Byju%20Raveendran%20breaking%20down%20in%20tears%20due%20to%20crises%20faced%20by%20the%20company%20came%20out%20in%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyju-founder-broke-down-in-tears-as-crises-engulfed-the-ed-tech-startup-4240392%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%20Byju's%20Founder%20Broke%20Down%20In%20Tears%20As%20Crises%20Engulfed%20Ed-Tech%20Startup%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran%20has%20faced%20crises%20for%20months.%20Apart%20from%20the%20raid%20by%20financial%20crime-fighting%20agency%2C%20the%20once%20high-flying%20tutoring%20start-up%20failed%20to%20file%20its%20financial%20accounts%20on%20time.%20Several%20US-based%20investors%20have%20accused%20Byju's%20of%20hiding%20half%20a%20billion%20dollars%2C%20prompting%20lawsuits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran's%20rise%20from%20a%20private%20tutor%20to%20the%20leader%20of%20a%20%2422%20billion%20company%20captivated%20global%20investors%2C%20including%20Sequoia%20Capital%2C%20Blackstone%20Inc%2C%20and%20Mark%20Zuckerberg's%20foundation.%20During%20the%20pandemic%2C%20he%20cornered%20a%20majority%20of%20the%20EdTech%20market%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20after%20classrooms%20reopened%2C%20concerns%20about%20Byju's%20finances%20pricked%20at%20the%20firm's%20reputation.%20Investors%20questioned%20why%20Raveendran%20delayed%20hiring%20a%20chief%20financial%20officer%20for%20years%20and%20acquired%20more%20than%20a%20dozen%20companies%20across%20the%20world%20at%20break-neck%20speed.%20Scores%20of%20employees%20have%20either%20left%20or%20been%20fired.%20Board%20members%20have%20resigned.%20And%20many%20teaching%20centres%20are%20nearly%20empty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Raveendran's%20supporters%20attribute%20his%20missteps%20to%20the%20enthusiasm%20and%20naivete%20of%20an%20inexperienced%20founder%20who%20grew%20too%20quickly.%20But%20critics%20say%20he%20acted%20recklessly%20by%20withholding%20information%20about%20finances%20and%20failing%20to%20rigorously%20audit%20accounts.%20In%20India's%20start-up%20world%2C%20many%20see%20Byju's%20as%20the%20highest-profile%20example%20of%20what%20happens%20when%20a%20business%20scales%20one%20of%20the%20fastest-growing%20economies%20during%20a%20boom%20but%20fails%20to%20plan%20for%20a%20bust.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690529340000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fe2v05l28_byju-bloomberg_625x300_07_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyju-raveendran-please-help-me-distraught-byjus-employee-breaks-down-in-tears-4247475%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22An%20employee%20of%20Byju's%20claimed%20in%20an%20emotional%20video%20posted%20to%20LinkedIn%20that%20the%20edtech%20company%20had%20been%20pressuring%20her%20to%20resign.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyju-raveendran-please-help-me-distraught-byjus-employee-breaks-down-in-tears-4247475%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyju-raveendran-please-help-me-distraught-byjus-employee-breaks-down-in-tears-4247475%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbyju-raveendran-please-help-me-distraught-byjus-employee-breaks-down-in-tears-4247475%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Have%20identified%20world-class%20tech%20partner%2C%20tying%20up%20with%20them%3A%20Anil%20Agarwal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690528972000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F24%2Ffull%2F1684892527-6366.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhave-identified-world-class-tech-partner-tying-up-with-them-anil-agarwal-123072800305_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BFor%20semiconductor%20we%20have%20identified%20world%20class%20partner%2C%20we%20have%20already%20identified%20a%20world%20class%20partner%20for%20technology%20and%20are%20in%20process%20of%20tying%20up%20with%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20at%20SemiconIndia%202023%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhave-identified-world-class-tech-partner-tying-up-with-them-anil-agarwal-123072800305_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhave-identified-world-class-tech-partner-tying-up-with-them-anil-agarwal-123072800305_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fhave-identified-world-class-tech-partner-tying-up-with-them-anil-agarwal-123072800305_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Can%20Bills%20Be%20Passed%20When...%5C%22%3A%20Congress%20Raises%20Query%20Ahead%20Of%20Delhi%20Bill%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20bill%20on%20control%20of%20Delhi%20bureaucrats%20is%20likely%20to%20come%20up%20on%20Monday%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20The%20Opposition%2C%20which%20is%20fighting%20it%20tooth%20and%20nail%2C%20has%20questioned%20if%20bills%20can%20be%20passed%20when%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%20is%20pending.%20In%20a%20tweet%20today%2C%20Congress's%20Manish%20Tewari%20cited%20a%20rule-book%20that%20suggests%20the%20opposite%2C%20and%20urged%20Speaker%20Om%20Birla%20to%20%26quot%3Bstart%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20no%20confidence%20motion%20without%20let%20or%20demur%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20a%20travesty%20to%20pass%20bills%20when%20the%20no%20confidence%20is%20still%20pending%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Speaker%20has%20indicated%20that%20traditionally%2C%20the%20date%20for%20debate%20and%20discussion%20is%20decided%20after%20consulting%20all%20parties%20and%20legislative%20business%20is%20not%20restricted%20in%20the%20intervening%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDismissing%20the%20Congress'%20objections%2C%20the%20Speaker%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20my%20view%2C%20the%20time%20available%20to%20the%20House%20between%20leave%20being%20granted%20by%20the%20House%20and%20moving%20of%20the%20motion%20of%20no%20confidence%20can%20be%20gainfully%20utilised%20by%20the%20House%20in%20debates%20and%20discussion.%20The%20House%20would%20agree%20that%20it%20is%20our%20constitutional%20duty%20to%20legislate%20and%20raise%20issues%20of%20public%20importance.%20Rule%20198%20also%20does%20not%20bar%20taking%20up%20of%20any%20legislative%20or%20other%20matters%20of%20public%20importance%20after%20leave%20to%20moving%20a%20motion%20of%20no%20confidence%20has%20been%20granted%20by%20the%20House.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20bills%20including%20the%20Jan%20Vishwas%20Bill%20were%20passed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20today.%20Another%20was%20passed%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20after%20the%20Opposition's%20no-confidence%20motion%20was%20accepted%20by%20the%20Speaker.%20Pointing%20to%20the%20bills%2C%20Mr%20Tewari%20quoted%20from%20%26quot%3BPractice%20and%20Procedure%20of%20Parliament%26quot%3B%20by%20MN%20Kaul%20and%20SL%20Shakhdhar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20leave%20of%20the%20house%20to%20the%20moving%20of%20a%20motion%20of%20'No%20confidence'%20has%20been%20granted%2C%20no%20substantive%20motion%20on%20Policy%20matters%20is%20to%20be%20brought%20before%20the%20house%20by%20the%20government%20till%20the%20motion%20of%20no%20confidence%20is%20not%20disposed%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20is%20likely%20next%20week%20too%2C%20but%20well%20after%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20August%201%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20-%20who%20has%20to%20respond%20to%20the%20debate%20--%20is%20expected%20to%20visit%20Maharashtra.%20So%20the%20no-confidence%20motion%20can%20be%20discussed%2C%20answered%20and%20voted%20on%20Wednesday%20and%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Monsoon%20Session%20of%20Parliament%20will%20continue%20till%20August%2011%20and%20the%20government%20has%20a%20long%20list%20of%20bills%20it%20needs%20to%20push%20through.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20controversial%20of%20them%20is%20the%20bill%20to%20replace%20the%20Ordinance%20that%20wrests%20power%20to%20control%20bureaucrats%20from%20the%20elected%20government%20of%20Delhi%2C%20which%20the%20Opposition%20is%20determined%20not%20to%20allow%20through%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20numbers%20indicate%20that%20the%20government%20is%20in%20a%20strong%20position.%20Today%2C%20the%20ruling%20YSR%20Congress%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20declared%20that%20it%20would%20back%20the%20government%20both%20in%20the%20No-Confidence%20Motion%20and%20the%20Delhi%20bill%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20numbers%20are%20stacked%20firmly%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Rajya%20Sabha%20currently%20has%20238%20members%2C%20with%20the%20majority%20mark%20at%20120.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20and%20its%20allies%20have%20105%20members%20and%20will%20have%20the%20support%20of%20nine%20YSRCP%20MPs.%20The%20ruling%20party%20is%20also%20confident%20of%20the%20support%20of%20five%20nominated%20and%20two%20independent%20MPs%2C%20which%20takes%20its%20numbers%20to%20121.%20Around%20105%20Opposition%20members%20are%20against%20the%20Delhi%20Ordinance.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690528800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2F5sfdtv6s_lok-sabha-ani_625x300_27_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-bills-be-passed-when-congress-raises-query-ahead-of-delhi-bill-4247269%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20bill%20on%20control%20of%20Delhi%20bureaucrats%20likely%20to%20come%20up%20on%20Monday%20in%20Lok%20Sabha.%20the%20Opposition%2C%20which%20is%20fighting%20it%20tooth%20and%20nail%2C%20has%20questioned%20if%20bills%20can%20be%20passed%20when%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20the%20government%20is%20pending.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-bills-be-passed-when-congress-raises-query-ahead-of-delhi-bill-4247269%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-bills-be-passed-when-congress-raises-query-ahead-of-delhi-bill-4247269%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fcan-bills-be-passed-when-congress-raises-query-ahead-of-delhi-bill-4247269%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22Humzilla%5C%22%3A%20Video%20Of%20Dubai%20Sheikh's%20Giant%20Hummer%20Goes%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20video%20going%20viral%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20Twitter%20(rebranded%20as%20X)%20shows%20a%20giant%20Hummer%2C%20with%20claims%20that%20it%20is%20three%20times%20bigger%20that%20the%20regular%20SUV.%20The%20old%20clip%20shows%20some%20people%20helping%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20giant%20vehicle%20back%20up%20on%20a%20road%20with%20police%20vehicles%20parked%20nearby%20and%20sirens%20blaring.%20Users%20who%20shared%20the%20clip%20say%20the%20Hummer%20H1%20'X3'%20belongs%20to%20Sheikh%20Hamad%20bin%20Hamdan%20al%20Nahyan%2C%20a%20member%20of%20the%20ruling%20royal%20family%20of%20the%20United%20Arab%20Emir