%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22MLC%3A%20Seattle%20Orcas%20beat%20Texas%20Super%20Kings%20to%20reach%20final%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690527913000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102195200%2Cimgsize-39096.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fmajor-league-cricket-seattle-orcas-beat-texas-super-kings-by-9-wickets-to-reach-final%2Farticleshow%2F102195286.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Quinton%20de%20Kock%20hit%20an%20unbeaten%2088%20as%20Seattle%20Orcas%20beat%20Texas%20Super%20Kings%20by%209%20wickets%20to%20become%20the%20first%20team%20to%20reach%20the%20final%20of%20the%20inaugural%20Major%20League%20Cricket%20at%20the%20Grand%20Prairie%20Stadium%20in%20Dallas%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A9%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Fnews%2Fmajor-league-cricket-seattle-orcas-beat-texas-super-kings-by-9-wickets-to-reach-final%2Farticleshow%2F102195286.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Blue%20Whale%20Washes%20Ashore%20In%20Rain-Hit%20Andhra%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tragic%20incident%2C%20a%20blue%20whale%20washed%20ashore%20at%20a%20beach%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Srikakulam%20on%20Thursday.%20According%20to%20local%20outlets%2C%20the%20whale%20is%20about%2025%20feet%20long%20and%20weighs%20five%20tons.%20Photos%20and%20videos%20from%20the%20scene%2C%20posted%20online%2C%20show%20people%20from%20nearby%20villages%20gathered%20at%20the%20beach%20to%20look%20at%20the%20deep-sea%20creature.%20The%20blue%20whale%20washed%20up%20on%20Meghavaram%20beach%20of%20Santabommali%20mandal%20in%20Srikakulam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocal%20fishermen%20say%20it's%20rare%20for%20a%20blue%20whale%20to%20be%20stranded%20on%20a%20beach%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20when%20the%20southern%20state%20is%20witnessing%20heavy%20rainfall%20for%20the%20past%20few%20days.%20According%20to%20India%20Meteorological%20Department%20(IMD)%2C%20eight%20places%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20including%20Srikakulam%2C%20received%207cm%20rain%20in%20the%20past%2024%20hours.%20The%20weather%20department%20also%20said%20that%20the%20low%20pressure%20area%20over%20west-central%20and%20adjoining%20northwest%20Bay%20of%20Bengal%20off%20north%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20south%20Odisha%20coasts%20continues%20to%20persist%2C%20and%20is%20yet%20to%20aggravate%20into%20a%20depression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20influence%20of%20this%20weather%20system%2C%20moderate%20rain%20is%20likely%20to%20occur%20in%20several%20places%20across%20coastal%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Rayalaseema%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFishermen%20have%20been%20advised%20not%20to%20venture%20into%20the%20sea%20as%20squally%20weather%20with%20wind%20speeds%20reaching%20up%20to%2045-55%20km%20per%20hour%20and%20also%20gusting%20up%20to%2065%20kmph%20are%20likely%20over%20west-central%20and%20adjoining%20northwest%20Bay%20of%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blue%20whale%20is%20the%20largest%20animal%20on%20the%20planet%2C%20weighing%20as%20much%20as%20200%20tons%20(the%20weight%20of%20approximately%2033%20elephants).%20It%20has%20a%20heart%20the%20size%20of%20a%20Volkswagen%20Beetle.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.worldwildlife.org%2Fspecies%2Fblue-whale%5C%22%3EWorld%20Wildlife%20Federation%3C%2Fa%3E%20(WWF)%2C%20the%20creature's%20%C2%A0stomach%20can%20hold%20one%20ton%20of%20krill%20and%20it%20needs%20to%20eat%20about%20four%20tons%20of%20krill%20each%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20blue%20whales%20are%20considered%20as%20the%20loudest%20animals%20on%20Earth%20-%20even%20louder%20than%20a%20jet%20engine.%20Their%20calls%20reach%20188%20decibels%2C%20w