0government%20has%20also%20agreed.%20I%20appeal%20to%20the%20House%20to%20rise%20above%20partisan%20interests%20and%20allow%20a%20short-duration%20discussion%20on%20Manipur%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Dhankar%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProceedings%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20were%20abruptly%20adjourned%20the%20day%20after%20a%20spat%20between%20Mr%20Dhankar%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Derek%20O'Brien.%20Mr%20Dhankhar%20adjourned%20the%20proceedings%20after%20the%20TMC%20leader%20interrupted%20him%20to%20protest%20the%20non-admission%20of%20notices%20given%20by%20opposition%20members%20to%20discuss%20the%20Manipur%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-seven%20MPs%20from%20several%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Congress%20and%20the%20DMK%2C%20have%20submitted%20notices%20to%20suspend%20the%20listed%20business%20in%20the%20Parliament%20and%20discuss%20the%20ongoing%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankhar%20reiterated%20that%20he%20has%20already%20approved%20a%20short-term%20discussion%20on%20the%20topic%20and%20requested%20that%20members%20discuss%20it%20under%20that%20rule.%20The%20Vice%20President%20then%20went%20on%20to%20speak%20about%20how%20the%20behavior%20of%20MPs%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20is%20seen%20by%20the%20global%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20Mr%20O'Brien%20stood%20up%2C%20thumped%20the%20desk%2C%20and%20urged%20the%20opposition%20parties%20to%20continue%20their%20efforts%20to%20introduce%20the%20motion%20that%20they%20have%20been%20trying%20to%20pass%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20parliament%20last%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Dhankar%20dubbed%20the%20Trinamool%20leader's%20actions%20as%20%26quot%3Btheatrics%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BShow%20respect%20to%20the%20chair.%20Don't%20thump%20the%20desk.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20O'Brien%20continued%20with%20his%20sloganeering%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20adjo