its-over-decade-high-regains-rs-2-trillion-m-cap-after-january-2008-123072800212_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22If%20India%20Is%20Serious%20About%20FATF%20Review%2C%20ED%20Director's%20Term%20Shouldn't%20Be%20its%20Prime%20Concern%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27085725%2FUntitled-design-17-2.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Thursday%20extended%20the%20tenure%20of%20the%20current%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20director%20up%20to%20September%2015%2C%20following%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20appeal%20for%20an%20extension%20till%20October%2015.%20The%20Union%20government%20had%20said%20this%20is%20required%20in%20view%20of%20peculiar%20circumstances%20as%20the%20country%20is%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20peer%20country%20review%20of%20a%20UN%20body%2C%20the%20Financial%20Action%20Task%20Force%20(FATF).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20which%20had%20earlier%20held%20that%20the%20extension%20in%20the%20director%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20was%20illegal%20while%20allowing%20him%20to%20continue%20up%20to%20July%2031%20so%20that%20the%20government%20could%20find%20his%20replacement%2C%20lambasted%20Solicitor%20General%20Tushar%20Mehta%20and%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CAre%20you%20saying%20all%20other%20officers%20are%20incompetent%3F%20Only%20one%20officer%20can%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%20The%20extension%20was%20nevertheless%20given%20in%20%E2%80%9Clarger%20public%20interest%E2%80%9D%20and%20for%20smooth%20functioning%20of%20the%20agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExperts%20are%20questioning%20whether%20the%20FATF%20review%20is%20a%20fig%20leaf.%20Finance%20ministry%20sources%20point%20out%20that%20rather%20than%20preparing%20reports%20for%20the%20FATF%2C%20the%20ED%20would%20be%20better%20served%20if%20its%20conviction%20rate%20in%20the%20various%20cases%20pending%20in%20court%20went%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20the%20last%20time%20the%20FATF%20took%20up%20a%20review%20of%20India%20was%20in%202013%2C%20when%20a%20mutual%20evaluation%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETen%20years%20later%2C%20the%20FATF%20will%20be%20looking%20at%20the%20ground%20situation%20now%2C%20or%20as%20SG%20Mehta%20told%20the%20court%20at%20a%20previous%20hearing%2C%20%E2%80%9CExperience%20has%20shown%20that%20having%20the%20laws%20in%20the%20books%20is%20not%20enough%2C%20the%20main%20focus%20is%20now%20on%20effectiveness.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEffectiveness%E2%80%9D%20is%20one%20challenge%20that%20remains%20ten%20years%20later.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20absence%20of%20any%20conviction%20for%20ML%20(money%20laundering)%2C%20and%20the%20high%20evidentiary%20standard%20untested%20before%20the%20courts%2C%20particularly%20in%20respect%20of%20the%20proof%20of%20the%20foreign%20predicate%20offence%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%202013%20FATF%20review%20report%20said%20quoting%20statistics%20from%20the%20ED%2C%20the%20lead%20agency%20for%20investigating%20money%20laundering.%20Trials%20were%20underway%20in%20courts%20at%20various%20stages%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20May%202013%2C%20India%20provided%20an%20update%20of%20the%20number%20of%20ML%20investigations%20and%20prosecutions%20underway.%20The%20number%20of%20ML%20investigations%20increased%20from%20798%20on%2031%20December%202009%20(at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20ME%20on-site%20visit)%2C%20to%201%20405%20on%2015%20December%202011%2C%20to%201%20510%20on%2031%20August%202012%2C%20to%201%20530%20on%2030%20November%202012%2C%20and%201%20561%20on%2030%20April%202013.%20After%20an%20increase%20in%20the%20number%20of%20ML%20prosecutions%20from%206%20on%2031%20December%202009%20to%2036%20on%2031%20March%202011%2C%20this%20number%20remained%20almost%20status%20quo%20in%202012%20(37%20on%2030%20November%202011%20to%2040%20on%2031%20August%20and%2042%20on%2030%20November%202012).%20India%20reported%20that%20in%20March%202013%2C%207%20new%20prosecution%20complaints%20were%20filed.%20India%20clarified%20that%20all%2049%20cases%20are%20at%20various%20stages%20of%20trial%20before%20the%20designated%20special%20courts%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20went%20on%20to%20point%20out%20that%20a%20total%20of%2049%20prosecution%20complaints%20had%20been%20filed%20and%20values%20of%20properties%20under%20attachment%20were%20%2465%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20had%20raised%20concerns%20about%20the%20conviction%20rate.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20absence%20of%20any%20ML%20conviction%20remains%20a%20serious%20effectiveness%20issue.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fextension-directorate-sk-mishra-enforcement%5C%22%3EExtension%20Directorate%3A%20Why%20Is%20the%20Union%20Govt%20Hell-Bent%20on%20Yet%20Another%20Term%20for%20S.K.%20Mishra%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20the%20FATF%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20lack%20of%20conviction%20in%20cases%20then%2C%20it%20will%20have%20much%20to%20worry%20about%20now%2C%20going%20by%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20performance%20statistics.%20Of%20the%20nearly%206%2C000%20cases%20filed%20since%20inception%2C%20there%20has%20been%20a%20conviction%20in%2024%20out%20of%20only%2025%20cases%20in%20which%20a%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20trial%20was%20completed.%20Or%20as%20the%20ED%20would%20like%20to%20see%20the%20glass%20as%20full%2C%20it%20has%20a%20conviction%20rate%20of%2094%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fhow-the-enforcement-directorate-has-become-an-excessive-directorate%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20between%202018-19%20and%202021-22%2C%20cases%20registered%20by%20the%20ED%20rose%20by%20505%25%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanherald.com%2Fnational%2F505-rise-in-cases-registered-by-ed-since-2018-1205886.html%5C%22%3Efrom%20195%20cases%20in%202018-19%2C%20to%201%2C180%20in%202021-22%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20number%20of%20searches%20the%20ED%20conducted%20rose%20by%20a%20huge%202%2C555%25%20between%202004-14%20and%202014-22.%20As%20per%20the%20Union%20finance%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20own%20data%2C%20112%20searches%20were%20carried%20out%20by%20the%20ED%20between%202004%20and%202014%2C%20resulting%20in%20attachment%20of%20alleged%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20worth%20Rs%205%2C346%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20had%20sent%20a%20questionnaire%20to%20the%20ED.%20There%20are%20several%20questions%20that%20it%20did%20not%20respond%20to.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20how%20many%20cases%20has%20investigation%20been%20completed%20so%20that%20trial%20can%20commence%3F%20How%20many%20cases%20have%20been%20registered%20and%20closed%20by%20way%20of%20discharging%20or%20quashing%20or%20acquittal%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20many%20accused%20have%20been%20discharged%20after%20a%20complaint%20was%20filed%20in%20court%3F%20Of%20the%20properties%20attached%2C%20how%20many%20have%20been%20confiscated%20so%20far%20by%20the%20ED%3F%20While%20the%20ED%20had%20broken%20its%20silence%20and%20sent%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20a%20lengthy%20response%2C%20it%20remained%20silent%20on%20these%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EContrary%20to%20what%20the%20government%20told%20the%20court%2C%20the%20lead%20officer%20for%20the%20review%2C%20sources%20point%20out%2C%20is%20additional%20secretary%20revenue%20Vivek%20Agarwal.%20He%20is%20also%20holding%20additional%20charge%20of%20the%20Financial%20Intelligence%20Unit%20(FIU).%20The%20FIU%20is%20a%20key%20department%20in%20the%20FATF%20review%20and%20the%20top%20post%20is%20vacant%20after%20Pankaj%20Mishra%20was%20prematurely%20repatriated%20in%202022%20after%20six%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EYet%20the%20Union%20government%2C%20in%20its%20affidavit%2C%20said%20the%20ED%20director%20is%20key.%20In%20an%20appeal%20filed%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20told%20the%20court%20that%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20extremely%20essential%20that%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20is%20in%20the%20state%20of%20full%20readiness%20during%20this%20period%20till%20on-site%20(visit%20in%20November.)%20During%20this%20period%2C%20agencies%20are%20often%20required%20to%20provide%20responses%2C%20statistics%2C%20case%20studies%20etc%20in%20short%20spans%20of%20time%20to%20provide%20better%20understanding%20to%20assessment%20team%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20this%20purpose%2C%20guidance%20and%20leadership%20at%20a%20very%20senior%20level%20is%20required%E2%80%A6The%20intricacies%20of%20complex%20money%20laundering%20investigation%20may%20also%20need%20to%20be%20explained%20to%20them%20which%20can%20be%20done%20only%20by%20a%20person%20with%20hands-on%20experience%E2%80%A6The%20present%20Director%2C%20Directorate%20of%20Enforcement%20has%20been%20engaged%20in%20preparation%20of%20documents%20%E2%80%A6since%20beginning%20of%20year%202020%2C%20accordingly%2C%20his%20continuation%20in%20this%20ardous%20and%20delicate%20process%20is%20essential.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20say%20a%20country%20is%20judged%20on%2040%20parameters%20relating%20to%20law%2C%20justice%2C%20revenue%2C%20banking%2C%20insurance%20etc.%20and%20another%20nine%20on%20terror%20financing.%20The%20ED%E2%80%99s%20remit%20is%20just%20one%20of%20many.%20%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.fatf-gafi.org%2Fen%2Fcountries%2Fdetail%2FIndia.html%5C%22%3EThe%20FATF%20website%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20the%20lead%20ministry%20or%20authority%20for%20FATF%20is%20the%20Department%20of%20Economic%20Affairs.%20The%20other%20key%20authorities%20are%20Central%20Board%20of%20Excise%20and%20Customs%2C%20FIU%20and%20Union%20law%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20review%20is%20within%20an%2018-month%20time%20frame%20and%20began%20early%20this%20year.%20The%20final%20report%20will%20not%20be%20submitted%20before%20the%20end%20of%202024.%20India%20is%20a%20rare%20country%20whose%20FATF%20review%20has%20been%20postponed%20at%20least%20once%20on%20account%20of%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20FATF%20had%20concluded%20in%202013%2C%20%E2%80%9COverall%2C%20India%20has%20reached%20a%20satisfactory%20level%20of%20compliance%20with%20all%20of%20the%20core%20and%20key%20recommendations%E2%80%A6%20Consequently%2C%20it%20is%20recommended%20that%20India%20is%20removed%20from%20the%20regular%20follow-up%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20for%20this%20was%20a%20large%20number%20of%20amendments%20to%20extant%20laws%20on%20money%20laundering%2C%20banking%20and%20terrorism.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690524052000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27085725%2FUntitled-design-17-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fif-india-is-really-concerned-about-fatf-review-ed-directors-term-shouldnt-be-its-prime-concern%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22During%20the%20previous%20FATF%20review%20in%202012%2C%20the%20ED's%20low%20conviction%20rate%20had%20been%20pointed%20out.%20That%20remains%20a%20challenge%20which%20the%20agency%20and%20government%20do%20not%20seem%20to%20be%20addressing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fif-india-is-really-concerned-about-fatf-review-ed-directors-term-shouldnt-be-its-prime-concern%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%20and%20Gauri%20hide%20face%2C%20avoid%20paps%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690523212000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102192223%2Cimgsize-36054.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshah-rukh-khan-and-gauri-hide-face-avoid-paps-as-they-exit-manager-pooja-dadlanis-house-see-photos%2Farticleshow%2F102192223.cms%22%2C%22summary