.%20China%20has%20repeatedly%20lobbied%20for%20expansion%20during%20those%20meetings%2C%20said%20the%20officials%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20as%20the%20discussions%20are%20private.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDozens%20of%20other%20nations%20are%20also%20clamoring%20to%20join%20the%20alliance%2C%20fueling%20western%20concerns%20the%20group%20is%20moving%20to%20become%20a%20counterweight%20to%20Washington%20and%20the%20European%20Union.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrazil%20wants%20to%20avoid%20expansion%20partly%20because%20of%20these%20worries%2C%20while%20India%20wants%20strict%20rules%20on%20how%20and%20when%20other%20nations%20could%20move%20closer%20to%20the%20group%2C%20without%20formally%20expanding%20it.%20Any%20decision%20will%20require%20consensus%20among%20the%20members%20who%20will%20meet%20Aug.%2022-24.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Brazil%20want%20to%20use%20the%20summit%20to%20discuss%20potentially%20bringing%20in%20additional%20countries%20with%20observer%20status%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%20South%20Africa%20supports%20discussing%20different%20membership%20options%20to%20accommodate%20this%2C%20but%20doesn't%20necessarily%20oppose%20expansion%2C%20two%20of%20the%20officials%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BRICS%20leaders%20meeting%20last%20year%20authorized%20the%20expansion%20of%20membership%2C%20adding%20more%20members%20to%20BRICS%20is%20the%20political%20consensus%20of%20the%20five%20BRICS%20countries%2C%26quot%3B%20China's%20foreign%20ministry%20said%20in%20a%20response%20to%20Bloomberg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20aims%20to%20showcase%20the%20bloc's%20goals%20to%20establish%20itself%20as%20a%20serious%20political%20and%20economic%20force.%20The%20group%20has%20already%20discussed%20the%20potential%20establishment%20of%20a%20common%20currency%2C%20although%20significant%20progress%20toward%20that%20goal%20isn't%20expected.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20summit%20comes%20at%20a%20time%20of%20heightened%20tensions%20between%20Washington%20and%20Beijing%2C%20and%20after%20South%20Africa%20fretted%20over%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin's%20attendance.%20He'll%20participate%20virtually%20so%20South%20Africa%20doesn't%20have%20to%20execute%20an%20International%20Criminal%20Court%20arrest%20warrant%20for%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRICS%20members%20have%20refused%20to%20join%20the%20likes%20of%20the%20Group%20of%20Seven%20in%20blaming%20and%20sanctioning%20Russia%20over%20its%20invasion%20of%20Ukraine%2C%20although%20the%20New%20Development%20Bank%20started%20by%20BRICS%20froze%20Russian%20projects%20and%20Moscow%20hasn't%20been%20able%20to%20access%20dollars%20via%20the%20bloc's%20shared%20foreign%20currency%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERussia%20does%20not%20hold%20a%20firm%20position%20on%20expanding%20BRICS%20said%20Fyodor%20Lukyanov%2C%20head%20of%20the%20Council%20on%20Foreign%20and%20Defense%20Policy%2C%20which%20advises%20the%20Kremlin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20broadly%20in%20favor%20of%20BRICS%20expansion%2C%20but%20without%20any%20huge%20enthusiasm.%20It's%20following%20the%20others'%20lead.%20We%20won't%20block%20any%20decision.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormed%20officially%20in%202009-2010%2C%20the%20bloc%20has%20struggled%20to%20have%20the%20kind%20of%20geopolitical%20influence%20that%20matches%20its%20collective%20economic%20reach.%20Current%20BRICS%20members%20represent%20more%20than%2042%25%20of%20the%20world's%20population%20and%20account%20for%2023%25%20of%20global%20gross%20domestic%20product%20and%2018%25%20of%20trade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDraft%20rules%20for%20admission%20to%20the%20group%20were%20drawn%20up%20after%20India's%20opposition%20to%20China's%20push%20for%20expansion%2C%20said%20two%20Indian%20officials.%20The%20guidelines%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20discussed%20and%20adopted%20during%20the%20leader's%20summit%20next%20month%2C%20the%20officials%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20has%20put%20forward%20the%20idea%20that%20BRICS%20nations%20should%20look%20to%20emerging%20economies%20as%20well%20as%20democracies%20like%20Argentina%20and%20Nigeria%20if%20they%20want%20to%20expand%20the%20group%2C%20rather%20than%20Saudi%20Arabia%2C%20with%20its%20dynastic%20and%20autocratic%20rule%2C%20one%20of%20the%20officials%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia's%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20discussed%20issues%20with%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20potential%20admission%20with%20the%20kingdom's%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammad%20bin%20Salman%20last%20month%2C%20the%20official%20said.%20The%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20in%20India%20didn't%20comment.%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20government%20didn't%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20BRICS%20would%20bolster%20Crown%20Prince%20Mohammed's%20attempts%20to%20diversify%20his%20nation's%20economy%2C%20an%20effort%20that%20has%20bought%20it%20closer%20to%20Russia%20and%20China%20in%20recent%20years.%20China%20is%20the%20kingdom's%20top%20oil%20customer%2C%20while%20it%20relies%20on%20relations%20with%20Russia%20for%20the%20OPEC%2B%20alliance.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Saudis%20are%20having%20their%20Asian%20moment%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Saudi%20analyst%20Salman%20Al-Ansari%2C%20who%20said%20bilateral%20trade%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20exponentially.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrazil%20is%20working%20quietly%20to%20avoid%20direct%20confrontation%20in%20the%20BRICS%20bloc%20and%20resist%20pressure%20from%20China%20to%20make%20it%20an%20antagonistic%20body%20that%20challenges%20the%20G7%2C%20a%20Brazilian%20official%20said.%20China%20has%20reiterated%20the%20request%20for%20expansion%20at%20all%20preparatory%20meetings%2C%20including%20two%20last%20week%20which%20took%20place%20virtually%2C%20the%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrazil's%20proposal%20is%20to%20create%20%26quot%3Bobserver%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bpartner%20country%26quot%3B%20categories.%20New%2