0in%20Mahabharata%20is%20that%20Gandhari's%20family%20didn't%20want%20her%20to%20marry%20Dhritarashtra.%20Bhisma%20Pitamah%20forced%20the%20marriage%20between%20them.%20Shakuni's%20brother%20was%20imprisoned%2C%20and%20later%20the%20mama%20took%20revenge.%20That%20is%20also%20love%20jihad.%20Gandhari's%20family%20objected%2C%20and%20as%20such%20she%20wore%20a%20cloth%20over%20her%20eyes.%20When%20Krishna%20came%20to%20take%20Rukmini%2C%20Arjun%20came%20in%20a%20different%20roop%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Borah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHimanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20condemned%20the%20Congress%20leader%20dragging%20Lord%20Krishna%20into%20the%20issue.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20against%20Sanatan%20Dharma%2C%20it%20is%20against%20Hindu%20Dharma%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20requests%20Mr%20Borah%20not%20to%20bring%20up%20Lord%20Krishna%20in%20the%20controversy%20like%20%26quot%3Bwe%20shouldn't%20drag%20Hajrat%20Mohammad%20or%20Jesus%20Christ%26quot%3B%20into%20any%20religious%20controversy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSecondly%2C%20what%20is%20love%20jihad%3F%20When%20a%20girl%20is%20married%20by%20false%20identity%20and%20is%20forced%20to%20change%20her%20religion%20after%20marriage.%20Lord%20Krishna%20never%20asked%20Rukmini%20to%20change%20her%20religion.%20If%20someone%20files%20a%20case%2C%20we%20will%20have%20to%20arrest%20the%20person%20who%20has%20said%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sarma%20said%2C%20without%20naming%20Mr%20Borah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E25-year-old%20Nazibur%20Rahman%20Bora%20on%20Wednesday%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhow-lockdown-love-story-ended-in-grisly-triple-murder-in-assam-4240391%5C%22%3Emurdered%20his%2024-year-old%20wife%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Sanghamitra%20Ghosh%2C%20and%20her%20parents%2C%20before%20surrendering%20to%20police%20with%20their%20nine-month-old%20baby%20in%20his%20arms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22hjeeicu%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%