n%2C%20but%20waking%20up%20on%20the%20wet%20grass%20in%20the%20morning%20wasn't%20very%20exciting%20for%20them%2C%20so%20I%20decided%20to%20build%20a%20deck%20for%20them%20to%20camp%20on%20for%20the%20next%20evening.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Two%20children%20help%20out%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20wooden%20frames%20for%20the%20glamping%20pods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b639d8db90260019356209%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreen's%20daughter%20and%20son%20help%20out%20with%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20wooden%20frames%20for%20the%20glamping%20pods.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20days%20turned%20into%20weeks%2C%20Green%20and%20his%20children%20%E2%80%94%20who%20were%20then%20six%20and%20eight%20years%20old%20%E2%80%94%20continued%20chipping%20away%20at%20their%20little%20DIY%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20kept%20building%20a%20little%20more%20each%20day%20with%20them%2C%20teaching%20them%20things%20and%20showing%20them%20how%20to%20do%20stuff.%20And%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20first%20lockdown%2C%20I%20had%20created%20what%20I%20now%20know%20to%20be%20a%20glamping%20pod%2C%26quot%3B%20Green%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20wooden%20frame%20of%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b639e5db9026001935620f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20wooden%20frame%20of%20one%20of%20the%20glamping%20pods.%3Cp%3EThe%20Secret%20Garden%20Glamping%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20lockdown%20DIY%20project%20went%20viral%20on%20the%20internet%20after%20it%20was%20picked%20up%20by%20an%20online%20publication.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople%20started%20messaging%20me%20thro