3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fcash-out-refinance%5C%22%3Ecash-out%20refinance%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20use%20the%20money%20for%20other%20purposes%20%E2%80%94%20renovations%2C%20for%20example%2C%20or%20sending%20kids%20to%20college%20%E2%80%94%20a%20low%20appraisal%20means%20there's%20less%20cash%20to%20draw%20from.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20this%20chronic%20undervaluing%20contributes%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-racism-has-cost-black-americans-black-tax-2020-9%5C%22%3Eracial%20wealth%20gap%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20a%20difference%20of%20over%20%24130%2C000%20between%20the%20accumulated%20wealth%20of%20a%20Black%20family%20and%20that%20of%20a%20white%20one%20according%20to%20a%202016%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.minneapolisfed.org%2Fresearch%2Finstitute-working-papers%2Fincome-and-wealth-inequality-in-america-1949-2016%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudy%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20Minneapolis%20on%20income%20and%20wealth%20inequality%20in%20America.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThe%20appraiser%20profession%20is%2095%25%20white%20in%20Philadelphia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESpence%20believes%20a%20lack%20of%20diversity%20in%20the%20appraiser%20profession%20is%20a%20primary%20reason%20for%20appraisal%20bias%2C%20she%20said.%20In%20her%20roughly%2010%20years%20selling%20homes%20in%20Philadelphia%20and%20the%20surrounding%20counties%2C%20she%20said%20she%20had%20never%20once%20seen%20an%20African%20American%20appraiser.%20She%20told%20Insider%3A%20%26quot%3BIt's%20as%20if%20they%20do%20not%20exist.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20surprising%2C%20considering%2095%25%20of%20appraisers%20in%20Philadelphia%20%E2%80%94%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.census.gov%2Fquickfacts%2Ffact%2Ftable%2Fphiladelphiacountypennsylvania%2FPST045222%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emajority%20nonwhite%20city%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20are%20white%2C%20a%20report%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fphlcouncil.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2FPhiladelphiaHomeAppraisalBiasTaskForce_Report_FINAL.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPhiladelphia%20Home%20Appraisal%20Bias%20Task%20Force%3C%2Fa%3E%20found.%20Nationally%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatausa.io%2Fprofile%2Fsoc%2Fappraisers-assessors-of-real-estate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20than%2090%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20appraisers%20are%20white%2C%20according%20to%20Data%20USA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Appraiser%20Qualifications%20Board%2C%20the%20national%20body%20that%20sets%20professional%20standards%20for%20appraiser%20education%20and%20licensing%2C%20is%20aware%20of%20the%20profession's%20diversity%20problem.%20The%20board's%20chair%2C%20Brad%20Swinney%2C%20told%20Insider%20he%20thought%20the%20main%20issue%20was%20the%20training%20framework.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20prospective%20appraisers%20are%20required%20to%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fappraisalfoundation.sharefile.com%2Fshare%2Fview%2Fs63f99dc2b9f241e0b3fd1645f7b63680%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E1%2C000%20hours%20or%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20experience%20(plus%20other%20requirements)%20to%20sit%20for%20a%20credential%20exam%20in%20residential-real-estate%20appraisal.%20Those%20hours%20must%20be%20completed%20under%20the%20supervision%20of%20a%20licensed%20appraiser%20and%20may%20be%20paid%20or%20unpaid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%2C%20Swinney%20said%2C%20has%20a%20negative%20effect%20on%20the%20appraiser%20pipeline%20because%20it%20creates%20%26quot%3Ban%20economic%20disincentive%20for%20an%20appraiser%20to%20take%20on%20a%20trainee.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20take%20them%20on%3B%20they%20lose%20money%20getting%20them%20trained%20up%2C%26quot%3B%20Swinney%20said%2C%20adding%3A%20%26quot%3BThere's%20a%20point%20at%20which%20they%20start%20to%20become%20viable%26quot%3B%20and%20get%20their%20credential%20soon%20after.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20you've%20introduced%20them%20to%20all%20your%20clients%2C%20taught%20them%20how%20they%20like%20the%20work%20done%2C%20and%20they're%20basically%20set%20up%20to%20take%20some%20of%20your%20clients%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Because%20of%20that%2C%20he%20added%2C%20appraisers%20tend%20to%20take%20on%20family%20members%20and%20friends%20as%20trainees%20since%20they're%20more%20likely%20to%20stay%20with%20the%20business%20%E2%80%94%20hence%20the%20lack%20of%20diversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EA%20new%20high-tech%20training%20program%20aims%20to%20widen%20the%20pipeline%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20counter%20that%2C%20the%20Appraiser%20Qualifications%20Board%20has%20approved%20a%20model%20for%20a%20computer%20program%2C%20called%20Practical%20Applications%20of%20Real%20Estate%20Appraisal%2C%20to%20satisfy%20the%20experience%20requirements%20of%20the%20credentials%20for%20a%20residential-real-estate%20appraiser.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPAREA%20programs%20can%20involve%20a%20variety%20of%20training%20methods%2C%20including%20computer-based%20learning%2C%20video%20gaming%2C%20video%20tutorials%2C%20and%20virtual%20reality.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20a%20flight%20simulator%20for%20appraisers%2C%26quot%3B%20Swinney%20said.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBSKmhRB1Uks%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEarly%20demonstrations%20of%20PAREA%3C%2Fa%3E%20show%20the%20user%20in%20virtual%20reality%20(using%20handsets%20and%20a%20VR%20headset)%20measuring%20a%20digitally%20rendered%20home%20and%20entering%20the%20measurements%20on%20a%20virtual%20tablet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hope%20is%20that%20getting%20rid%20of%20the%20supervisory%20requirement%20will%20open%20up%20the%20field%20to%20those%20who%20are%20otherwise%20qualified%20but%20can't%20land%20a%20supervisor%2C%20Swinney%20said.%20The%20Appraiser%20Qualifications%20Board%20has%20also%20added%20a%20requirement%20for%20prospective%20appraisers%20to%20gain%20education%20in%20fair-housing%20law%2C%20with%20an%20eye%20to%20ending%20appraisal%20bias.%20This%20field%20of%20study%20will%20become%20mandatory%20in%202026%2C%20Swinney%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERight%20now%2C%20Pennsylvania%20is%20among%20the%2042%20states%20that%20have%20signaled%20PAREA%20is%20an%20acceptable%20model%20for%20training%20appraisers.%20It%20wouldn't%20replace%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dos.pa.gov%2FProfessionalLicensing%2FBoardsCommissions%2FCertifiedRealEstateAppraisers%2FPages%2FCertified-Residential-Real-Estate-Appraiser-Licensure-Requirements-Snapshot.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPennsylvania's%20current%20licensing%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20would%20offer%20an%20alternative%20to%20the%20traditional%20supervisor-trainee%20model.%20The%20state's%20Board%20of%20Certified%20Real%20Estate%20Appraisers%20voted%20in%20September%20to%20begin%20a%20rulemaking%20process%20to%20allow%20PAREA%20to%20become%20available%20to%20prospective%20appraisers.%20The%20Pennsylvania%20Department%20of%20State%20said%20that%20process%20could%20take%20about%20a%20year%20to%20complete.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EPhiladelphia's%20mayoral%20favorite%20plans%20to%20prioritize%20equitable%20home%20appraisal%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ECherelle%20Parker%2C%20the%20Democratic%20nominee%20for%20Philadelphia's%20next%20mayor%20and%20the%20favorite%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbillypenn.com%2F2023%2F05%2F16%2Fphiladelphia-mayor-winner-may-primary-election-results%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewin%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%20she's%20committed%20to%20bringing%20an%20end%20to%20appraisal%20bias%20in%20Philly.%20As%20a%20City%20Council%20member%2C%20she%20formed%20the%20Home%20Appraisal%20Bias%20Task%20Force%2C%20which%20produced%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fphlcouncil.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F07%2FPhiladelphiaHomeAppraisalBiasTaskForce_Report_FINAL.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereport%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20recommendations%20for%20and%20data%20on%20appraisal%20bias%20in%20the%20city.%20Parker%20said%20the%20task%20force%20would%20continue%20its%20work%20under%20her%20leadership.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20mayor%2C%20I%20will%20be%20working%20to%20ensure%20that%20local%2C%20state%2C%20and%20federal%20solutions%20are%20implemented%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20for%20bias%20in%20appraisals%20but%20also%20for%20other%20fair-housing%20issues%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BBuying%20a%20home%20is%20the%20largest%20investment%20many%20Philadelphians%20will%20ever%20make%2C%20and%20we%20must%20provide%20more%20opportunities%20for%20Philadelphians%20to%20own%20their%20own%20homes%20and%20realize%20the%20true%20value%20and%20return%20on%20that%20investment.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpence%2C%20the%20real-estate%20broker%2C%20said%20she's%20more%20than%20ready%20for%20change%20to%20come%2C%20whether%20it's%20through%20legislation%2C%20PAREA%2C%20or%20something%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20absolutely%2C%20100%25%2C%20need%20change%20in%20the%20appraisal%20system%2C%26quot%3B%20Spence%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20can't%20wait.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20African%20Americans%20and%20the%20gap%2C%20it's%20always%2C%20'Oh%2C%20you%20have%20to%20wait%20your%20turn.%20Change%20doesn't%20happen%20overnight.'%20But%20we've%20been%20waiting%20a%20long%20time.%20We've%20been%20waiting%20centuries%20for%20change%20and%20equality%2C%20and%20I%20think%20now%20is%20the%20time%20for%20us%20to%20get%20equality.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcomputer-program-track-end-home-appraisal-racial-bias-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20I