andard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-group-lenders-may-offer-750-million-loan-for-ambuja-debt-123072701282_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fadani-group-lenders-may-offer-750-million-loan-for-ambuja-debt-123072701282_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explainer%3A%20Pakistan%20Has%20Just%20Given%20More%20Powers%20to%20Its%20Caretaker%20Government.%20And%20It%20Is%20Not%20Good%20News%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24215513%2F6483091829_b0a9599ab5_k.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20With%20a%20joint%20session%20of%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20parliament%20handing%20over%20more%20powers%20to%20a%20caretaker%20government%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20July%2026%2C%20questions%20are%20being%20raised%20over%20whether%20the%20general%20elections%20would%20be%20held%20in%20October%20as%20per%20the%20constitutional%20provisions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20is%20a%20short%20explainer%20on%20why%20the%20legislative%20changes%20have%20led%20to%20concerns%20that%20elections%20will%20be%20delayed%20and%20any%20polls%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98empowered%E2%80%99%20caretaker%20government%20may%20not%20be%20an%20answer%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20chronic%20political%20instability.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20caretaker%20system%20of%20Pakistan%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-up%20to%20the%20general%20elections%2C%20some%20democratically%20elected%20governments%20transition%20into%20a%20%E2%80%98caretaker%E2%80%99%20mode%2C%20wherein%20their%20powers%20are%20severely%20limited.%20In%20India%2C%20a%20code%20of%20conduct%20is%20supposed%20to%20come%20into%20force%20after%20the%20Election%20Commission%20announces%20the%20poll%20dates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Pakistan%20is%20almost%20unique%20in%20institutionalising%20the%20practice%20of%20appointing%20non-elected%20officials%20to%20head%20caretaker%20governments.%20Bangladesh%20had%20also%20drawn%20up%20guidelines%20for%20caretaker%20governments%2C%20but%20the%20provision%20was%20removed%20from%20the%20constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%20has%20a%20long%20history%20of%20holding%20elections%20under%20%E2%80%9Cneutral%E2%80%9D%20candidates%2C%20but%20they%20have%20all%20been%20highly%20contentious.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202012%2C%20electoral%20reforms%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F696880%5C%22%3Ewere%20introduced%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20removing%20the%20power%20of%20the%20president%20to%20appoint%20a%20caretaker%20prime%20minister%20or%20chief%20minister.%20The%2020th%20amendment%20established%20that%20if%20the%20prime%20minister%20and%20the%20leader%20of%20opposition%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20decide%20on%20the%20name%20of%20the%20caretaker%20prime%20minister%2C%20then%20the%20decision%20would%20be%20taken%20by%20a%20parliamentary%20committee.%20The%20committee%20is%20made%20up%20of%20equal%20number%20of%20lawmakers%20from%20the%20ruling%20side%20and%20the%20opposition.%20However%2C%20if%20the%20committee%20also%20fails%20to%20reach%20a%20decision%2C%20then%20the%20Election%20Commission%20will%20take%20the%20decision%20within%20two%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20were%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fna.gov.pk%2Fuploads%2Fdocuments%2F1506961151_781.pdf%5C%22%3EElection%20Act%20of%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20caretaker%20government%20had%20to%20support%20the%20Election%20Commission%20in%20holding%20the%20polls%2C%20as%20well%20as%20keep%20the%20government%20ticking%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20had%20strict%20instructions%20that%20the%20caretaker%20government%20shall%2C%20as%20per%20section%20230%20(1)%2C%20%E2%80%9Crestrict%20itself%20to%20activities%20that%20are%20of%20routine%2C%20non-controversial%20and%20urgent%2C%20in%20the%20public%20interest%20and%20reversible%20by%20the%20future%20government%20elected%20after%20the%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%2C%20section%20230%20(2)%20had%20provisions%20that%20the%20interim%20government%20cannot%20take%20%E2%80%9Cmajor%20policy%20decisions%20except%20on%20urgent%20matters%E2%80%9D%20and%20neither%20enter%20into%20%E2%80%9Cmajor%20international%20negotiation%20with%20any%20foreign%20country%20or%20international%20agency%20or%20sign%20or%20ratify%20any%20international%20binding%20instrument%20except%20in%20an%20exceptional%20case%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20were%20the%20changes%20unveiled%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Pakistan%20Prime%20Minister%20Shehbaz%20Sharif%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Fworld%2Fwill-hand-over-charge-to-caretaker-government-in-august-pak-pm-shehbaz-sharif%2F1668529%2F%5C%22%3Eannounced%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20will%20hand%20over%20the%20reins%20of%20the%20government%20to%20a%20caretaker%20government%20in%20August.%20The%20move%20immediately%20triggered%20feverish%20speculation%20over%20the%20identity%20of%20the%20caretaker%20prime%20ministers%2C%20with%20the%20politicking%20taking%20place%20in%20Dubai%20and%20London%20where%20the%20heads%20of%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20are%20camped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20a%20slew%20of%20reports%20that%20claimed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1766399%2Fn-proposes-dar-as-interim-pm-but-ppp-disagrees%5C%22%3Efinance%20minister%20Ishaq%20Dar%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20whose%20son%20is%20married%20to%20Pakistan%20Muslim%20League%20(Nawaz)%20party%20chief%20Nawaz%20Sharif%E2%80%99s%20daughter%20%E2%80%93%20would%20be%20the%20head%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20the%20current%20Leader%20of%20Opposition%20in%20the%20National%20Assembly%20is%20a%20Pakistan%20Tehreek-e-Insaf%20(PTI)%20dissident%20lawmaker%2C%20who%20had%20been%20part%20of%2020%20PTI%20members%20that%20had%20joined%20the%20opposition%20in%20passing%20a%20no-confidence%20motion%20against%20then%20Prime%20Minister%20Imran%20Khan%20in%20March%202022.%20Therefore%2C%20the%20choice%20for%20heading%20the%20caretaker%20government%20would%20be%20an%20exercise%20for%20the%20ruling%20parties%2C%20despite%20the%20guidelines%20on%20paper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDar%E2%80%99s%20name%20was%20quickly%20shot%20down%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party.%20Nevertheless%2C%20Pakistan%20came%20to%20know%20about%20the%20impending%20changes%20to%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%20only%20from%20his%20appearance%20on%20a%20television%20channel.%20When%20asked%20whether%20section%20230%20of%20the%20Election%20Act%20would%20be%20modified%2C%20he%20replied%2C%20%E2%80%9CTo%20the%20best%20of%20my%20understanding%2C%20yes.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistan-india-imran-khan-manipur-karnataka%5C%22%3EFrom%20Pakistan%2C%20a%20Message%20for%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20was%20the%20amendment%20passed%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Pakistan%20government%20on%20July%2025%20proposed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2427955%2F54-amendments-proposed-to-election-act%5C%22%3E54%20amendments%20to%20the%20Election%20Act%2C%202017%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20including%20upgrading%20the%20powers%20that%20will%20allow%20the%20caretaker%20government%20to%20take%20decisions%20with%20regard%20to%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20government%20was%20forced%20to%20defer%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20by%20a%20day%20when%20both%20political%20allies%20and%20the%20opposition%20claimed%20at%20the%20joint%20session%20of%20parliament%20that%20there%20was%20a%20last%20minute%20addition%20to%20the%20clause%20that%20would%20enlarge%20the%20scope%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government%20to%20decide%20on%20%E2%80%9Curgent%20matters%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20opposing%20lawmakers%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20new%20changes%20were%20not%20even%20discussed%20in%20the%20closed-door%20meetings%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20on%20electoral%20reforms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20ahead%20of%20the%20Wednesday%20(July%2026)%20meeting%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%20met%20with%20the%20government%20and%20was%20able%20to%20persuade%20its%20allies%2C%20with%20a%20slightly%20altered%20amendment.%20However%2C%20the%20opposition%20remained%20unconvinced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftribune.com.pk%2Fstory%2F2427994%2Fjoint-session-approves-election-act-amendments-empowering-caretaker-setup%5C%22%3EThe%20%3Cem%3EExpress%20Tribune%3C%2Fem%3E%20described%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20passage%20of%20the%20Bill%20by%20a%20voice%20vote%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstunning%20display%20of%20legislative%20acrobatics%E2%80%9D%20that%20has%20re-drawn%20the%20lines%20of%20political%20authority%20in%20Pakistan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20does%20the%20amendment%20say%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDue%20to%20the%20outcry%20in%20parliament%2C%20Pakistan%20law%20minister%20Azam%20Nazeer%20Tarar%20admitted%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20joint%20sitting%20of%20parliament%20that%20the%20amendment%20had%20not%20been%20discussed%20during%20the%20meeting%20of%20the%20parliamentary%20committee%2C%20but%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20posted%20on%20the%20panel%E2%80%99s%20WhatsApp%20group%20five%20days%20earlier.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20minister%20said%20that%20amendment%20still%20allows%20the%20caretaker%20government%20to%20address%20%E2%80%9Curgent%20matters%E2%80%9D%2C%20but%20has%20dropped%20the%20provision%20on%20allowing%20transfers%20and%20promotions%2C%20following%20the%20strong%20objections%20raised%20earlier%20on%20Wednesday%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20approved%20amendment%2C%20as%20per%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1767041%2Fhue-and-cry-leads-govt-to-dilute-powers-for-caretakers%5C%22%3Emedia%20reports%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20adds%20a%20rider%20to%20section%20230(2)%3A%20%E2%80%9CProvided%20that%20sub-sections%20(1)%20and%20(2)%20shall%20not%20apply%20where%20the%20caretaker%20government%20has%20to%20take%20actions%20or%20decisions%20regarding%20existing%20bilateral%20or%20multilateral%20agreements%20or%20the%20projects%20already%20initiated%20under%20the%20Public%20Private%20Partnership%20Authority%20Act%2C%202017%20(VIII%20of%202017)%2C%20the%20Inter-Governmental%20Commercial%20Transactions%20Act%2C%202022%20(XXX%20of%202022)%20and%20the%20Privatisation%20Commission%20Ordinance%2C%202000%20(LII%20of%202000).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20sub-sections%20had%20outlined%20the%20limitations%20of%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fpakistans-precarious-path-from-hero-worship-to-economic-desperation%5C%22%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20Precarious%20Path%3A%20From%20Hero%20Worship%20to%20Economic%20Desperation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20official%20argument%20for%20%E2%80%98empowering%E2%80%99%20the%20caretaker%20government%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20the%20International%20Monetary%20Fund%E2%80%99s%20(IMF)%20board%20approved%20a%20nine-month%20standby%20arrangement%20for%20%243%20billion%2C%20which%20has%20since%20opened%20more%20doors%20to%20bilateral%20donors.%20During%20the%20joint%20session%2C%20the%20Pakistani%20law%20minister%20claimed%20that%20giving%20more%20powers%20to%20the%20caretaker%20government%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.geo.tv%2Flatest%2F501392-pml-ns-move-seeking-unbridled-powers-for-caretakers-faces-opposition-from-allies%5C%22%3Eensure%20the%20continuity%20of%20measures%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20were%20agreed%20upon%20with%20the%20IMF%20as%20the%20same%20could%20not%20be%20put%20in%20cold%20storage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJamaat-I-Islami%20senator%20Senator%20Mushtaq%20Ahmed%20claimed%20that%20it%20was%20regrettable%20that%20the%20IMF%20was%20even%20influencing%20electoral%20laws.%20He%20described%20it%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Csoft%20coup%E2%80%9D%2C%20that%20put%20question%20marks%20on%20the%20conduct%20of%20the%20general%20elections.%20Ahmed%20also%20articulated%20that%20the%20insidious%20reason%20for%20the%20amendment%20might%20be%20to%20delay%20the%20elections%20by%20extending%20the%20term%20of%20the%20caretaker%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPakistan%E2%80%99s%20minister%20for%20economic%20affairs%2C%20Sardar%20Ayaz%20Sadiq%2C%20dismissed%20the%20allegation%20that%20it%20would%20mean%20that%20the%20caretaker%20government%20would%20remain%20at%20the%20helm%20for%20a%20longer%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20the%20powers%20of%20the%20caretakers%20under%20the%20re-drafted%20amendment%20had%20been%20restricted%20to%20ongoing%20multilateral%20and%20bilateral%20projects%2C%20and%20they%20would%20not%20have%20the%20mandate%20to%20initiate%20new%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20has%20been%20the%20reception%20to%20the%20move%20to%20a%20Caretaker%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98empowerment%E2%80%99%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20editorial%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20News%3C%2Fem%3E%20pointed%20out%20that%20the%20talk%20about%20the%20name%20of%20PML-N%E2%80%99s%20Ishaq%20Dar%20and%20others%20had%20started%20to%20gather%20momentum%20when%20the%20ruling%20Pakistan%20Democratic%20Movement%20(PDM)%20coalition%20realised%20that%20the%20interim%20government%20could%20be%20prolonged%20for%20than%20the%2060%20or%2090%20days%20it%20is%20supposed%20to%20remain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20important%20to%20note%20that%20there%20is%20little%20justification%20for%20the%20whole%20constitution%20to%20be%20upended%20for%20the%20mere%20possibility%20that%20the%20interim%20setup%20could%20continue%20beyond%20its%20mandated%20time%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20newspaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20editorial%20criticised%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20for%20going%20back%20on%20its%20position%20enshrined%20in%20the%202006%20Charter%20of%20Democracy%2C%20which%20advocated%20for%20neutral%20caretaker%20governments%20to%20conduct%20elections%2C%20by%20having%20a%20politician%20to%20head%20the%20interim%20set-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20prolonged%20caretaker%20setup%20has%20no%20constitutional%20justification%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20why%20on%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20list%20of%20things%20to%20do%20at%20the%20moment%20should%20be%3A%20a%20neutral%20caretaker%20setup%2C%20and%20free%20and%20fair%20elections.%20Everything%20else%20falls%20into%20place%20after%20that%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20editorial.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dawn.com%2Fnews%2F1766897%2Fcaretaker-conundrum%5C%22%3EWriting%20in%20the%20%3Cem%3EDawn%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Zahid%20Hussain%20wrote%20that%20two%20months%20were%20not%20a%20long%20period%20that%20%E2%80%9Cpolicy%20decisions%20cannot%20wait%E2%80%9D.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20move%20also%20fuels%20speculation%20about%20elections%20not%20being%20held%20within%20the%20stipulated%20time%20frame.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWarning%20that%20their%20alignment%20with%20the%20security%20establishment%20to%20dismantle%20PTI%20will%20haunt%20the%20political%20parties%2C%20Hussain%20noted%20that%20tainted%20elections%20under%20a%20partisan%20caretaker%20administration%20will%20aggravate%20an%20already%20combustible%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20the%20elections%2C%20which%20are%20supposed%20to%20strengthen%20the%20democratic%20process%20and%20provide%20political%20stability%2C%20may%20result%20in%20the%20country%20plunging%20deeper%20into%20chaos%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMudassar%20Rizvi%2C%20who%20has%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20watchdog%20Free%20and%20Fair%20Election%20Network%20(Fafen)%2C%20wrote%20that%20the%20political%20consequences%20of%20this%20amendment%20and%20the%20delay%20in%20holding%20elections%20to%20Punjab%20and%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20assemblies%20beyond%2090%20days%20%E2%80%9Chave%20reinforced%20the%20view%20that%20efforts%20are%20afoot%20to%20put%20together%20a%20caretaker%20dispensation%20with%20an%20aim%20greater%20than%20simply%20holding%20the%20next%20general%20elections%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690476231000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F24215513%2F6483091829_b0a9599ab5_k.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fexplainer-pakistan-has-just-given-more-powers-to-its-caretaker-government-and-it-is-not-good-news%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Why%20the%20legislative%20changes%20have%20led%20to%20concerns%20that%20elections%20will%20be%20delayed%20and%20any%20polls%20under%20the%20%E2%80%98empowered%E2%80%99%20caretaker%20government%20may%20not%20be%20an%20answer%20to%20Pakistan%E2%80%99s%20chronic%20political%20instability.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fexplainer-pakistan-has-just-given-more-powers-to-its-caretaker-government-and-it-is-not-good-news%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%221st%20ODI%3A%20Surya%20makes%20Samson%20presence%20felt%20despite%20not%20in%20playing%20XI%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690476167000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102179912%2Cimgsize-37080.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Findia-in-west-indies%2F1st-odi-suryakumar-yadav-makes-sanju-samson-presence-felt-despite-not-in-playing-eleven%2Farticlesh