ftware%20developer%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20region%2C%20was%20deeply%20saddened%20by%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20village%20Nadiyam%20was%20one%20of%20the%2090%20villages%20impacted%20by%20the%20cyclone%2C%20resulting%20in%20complete%20destruction%20of%20the%20agricultural%20lands.%20This%20forced%20farmers%20to%20migrate%20to%20cities%20for%20livelihood.%20Interestingly%2C%20while%20many%20of%20Nimal%E2%80%99s%20friends%20decided%20to%20settle%20abroad%20due%20to%20the%20cyclone%E2%80%99s%20havoc%2C%20he%20chose%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F312716%2Fvibha-tripathi-advait-kumar-started-boon-install-drinking-water-atm-in-villages-gurugram%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20different%20path%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20stayed%20in%20his%20homeland.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%2035%20years%20old%2C%20Nimal%20left%20his%20job%20in%20Dubai%20to%20restore%20his%20hometown%E2%80%99s%20former%20prosperity.%20His%20first%20priority%20was%20reviving%20Peravurani%20lake%2C%20which%20could%20irrigate%20more%20than%206%2C000%20acres%20of%20farmland.%20The%20project%20required%20Rs%2032%20lakh%2C%20and%20with%20the%20help%20of%20like-minded%20volunteers%2C%20he%20planted%2025%2C000%20saplings%20across%20the%20Kaveri%20delta%20region.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20social%20media%20campaign%20%23BounceBackDelta%20was%20an%20attempt%20to%20help%20all%20those%20affected%20by%20the%20cyclone%20with%20clothes%2C%20groceries%2C%20household%20necessities%2C%20and%20money.%20The%20other%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F303262%2Fiit-roorkee-professor-technology-to-remove-arsenic-contamination-purify-drinking-water%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprojects%20taken%20up%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20his%20team%20include%20the%20Miyawaki%20plantation%2C%20a%20mangrove%20forest%20plantation%2C%20as%20well%20as%20rainwater%20harv