mpanies%2Fnews%2Fdemerged-hotels-biz-will-have-a-strong-balance-sheet-itc-chairman-123072701035_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fdemerged-hotels-biz-will-have-a-strong-balance-sheet-itc-chairman-123072701035_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Has%20the%20INDIA%20Alliance%20Made%20PM%20Modi%20Nervous%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13160506%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-4.04.26.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20is%20scared%20of%20INDIA%20(Indian%20National%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance).%20The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20under%20pressure%2C%E2%80%9D%20Nitish%20Kumar%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F260723%2Fnitish-seeks-modis-statement-on-manipur-violence.html%5C%22%3Etold%20reporters%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20Patna%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20July%2026%2C%20at%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20government%20function.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20was%20pointed%20out%20that%20Modi%20had%20compared%20INDIA%20with%20the%20East%20India%20Company%20and%20the%20Indian%20Mujahideen%2C%20the%20Bihar%20chief%20minister%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20are%20the%20manifestation%20of%20his%20nervousness%E2%80%A6%20he%20is%20under%20the%20spell%20of%20anxiety.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%20simply%20summarised%20the%20overwhelming%20sentiment%20of%20the%20INDIA%20leaders%2C%20drawn%20from%20different%20parties%20and%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20The%20opposition%20parties%20%E2%80%93%20after%20their%20successful%20meets%20at%20Patna%20and%20Bangaluru%20%E2%80%93%20have%20demonstrated%20superb%20floor%20coordination%20in%20both%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20and%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20protracted%20violence%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EModi%2C%20of%20course%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fnarendra-modi-talked-about-the-manipur-violence-but-did-he-really%5C%22%3Ebroke%20his%20silence%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20the%20issue%20%E2%80%93%2079%20days%20after%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20began.%20But%20he%20spoke%20outside%20parliament%2C%20and%20only%20about%20a%20viral%20video%20in%20which%20two%20Kuki%20women%20were%20paraded%20naked%20and%20attempted%20to%20link%20it%20with%20crimes%20against%20women%20in%20Chhattisgarh%20and%20Rajasthan.%20That%20has%20angered%20the%20opposition%20more.%20They%20have%20continuously%20stalled%20the%20proceedings%20in%20both%20the%20Houses%20ever%20since%20it%20assembled%20for%20the%20monsoon%20session%20on%20July%2020%20and%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fwhy-a-no-confidence-motion-now-four-tactical-advantages-the-opposition-might-be-aiming-for%5C%22%3Ebrought%20a%20no-cofidence%20motion%3C%2Fa%3E%20against%20the%20government.%20Their%20primary%20demand%20is%20that%20the%20PM%20must%20make%20a%20statement%20on%20Manipur%20in%20both%20the%20houses.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhy%20is%20Narendra%20Modi%20shying%20away%20from%20discussing%20the%20Manipur%20issue%20in%20the%20parliament%3F%20Why%20is%20Modi%20%E2%80%9Canxious%20and%20scared%E2%80%9D%2C%20as%20Nitish%20claims%3F%20Why%20did%20he%20choose%20to%20equate%20INDIA%20with%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20and%20the%20British%20East%20India%20Company%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20conversation%20with%20a%20cross-section%20of%20INDIA%20leaders%20brought%20to%20the%20fore%20two%20reasons%20they%20believe%20are%20behind%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20actions.%20First%2C%20the%20Union%20government%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cincompetence%E2%80%9D%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20problems%20besetting%20the%20country%20and%20secondly%20the%20tag%20of%20corruption%20now%20%E2%80%9Csticking%E2%80%9D%20to%20the%20BJP%20governments%20at%20the%20centre%20as%20well%20as%20states%20under%20its%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Incompetence%20and%20corruption%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20attempts%20by%20the%20government%20and%20the%20BJP%20to%20downplay%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20unabated%20violence%20%E2%80%93%20abd%20particularly%20the%20video%20showing%20the%20assault%20on%20the%20women%20%E2%80%93%20has%20shaken%20the%20conscience%20of%20the%20nation.%20It%20has%20also%20%E2%80%9Cexposed%E2%80%9D%20the%20PM%E2%80%99s%20incompetence%2C%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20say.%20That%20Manipur%20has%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20much%20vaunted%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20engine%E2%80%9D%20government%20with%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%20as%20its%20chief%20minister%20is%20another%20blow%20to%20the%20party.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20has%20exacerbated%20this%20feeling%20of%20%E2%80%9Cincompetence%E2%80%9D%20is%20the%20claim%2C%20made%20by%20human%20rights%20bodies%2C%20civil%20rights%20activists%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSAHtkiAiI78%5C%22%3Epublic%20intellectuals%3C%2Fa%3E%20operating%20in%20Northeast%2C%20that%20the%20Hindutva%20party%20pitted%20the%20two%20ethnic%20groups%20%E2%80%93%20the%20majority%20Meiteis%20against%20the%20minority%20Kukis%20%E2%80%93%20against%20each%20other.%20This%20was%20similar%20to%20what%20Modi%20did%20with%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20and%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20this%20template%2C%20the%20RSS-BJP%20strategists%2C%20working%20under%20the%20stewardship%20of%20Modi%20and%20Union%20home%20minister%20Amit%20Shah%2C%20calculated%20that%20they%20would%20establish%20the%20dominance%20of%20the%20Meiteis%20over%20the%20Kukis%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20strategy%20has%20backfired%20in%20Manipur%2C%20after%20the%20video%20emerged.%20The%20Kukis%20have%20repeatedly%20accused%20the%20Biren%20Singh%20government%20of%20siding%20with%20the%20Meitei%20community%20in%20a%20flagrantly%20biased%20manner.%20The%20Kuki%20women%20in%20the%20viral%20video%20said%20the%20state%20police%2C%20who%20were%20present%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fmanipur-police-women-video-paraded-naked%5C%22%3Edid%20not%20act%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20the%20mob%20stripped%20them%20naked%20and%20allegedly%20raped%20one%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20is%20already%20under%20fire%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20now%20for%20its%20dire%20failure%20in%20checking%20price-rise%2C%20unemployment%20and%20failing%20on%20its%20promises%20of%20getting%20houses%20for%20all%20by%202022%20and%20doubling%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income.%20The%20issues%20of%20unemployment%2C%20rural%20poverty%20and%20price%20rise%20have%2C%20apparently%2C%20slipped%20beyond%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F26170827%2FUntitled-design-16-2-1024x576.jpg%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-665264%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22675%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EVideo%20screengrab%20showing%20PM%20Modi%20with%20his%20back%20to%20the%20cameras%20after%20he%20addressed%20the%20Manipur%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20point%20that%20is%20said%20to%20rattled%20Modi%20and%20his%20party%20is%20that%20corruption%20is%20increasingly%20being%20associated%20with%20the%20BJP.%20The%20perception%20that%20the%20party%20used%20its%20money%20power%20to%20topple%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%20has%20gained%20ground%20all%20across%20the%20country.%20What%20has%20strengthened%20the%20perception%20is%20the%20Supreme%20Court%E2%80%99s%20declaration%20of%20the%20events%20that%20led%20to%20the%20Thackeray%E2%80%99s%20downfall%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-shiv-sena-uddhav-thackeray-eknath-shinde%5C%22%3Eillegal%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D.%20But%20even%20after%20the%20apex%20court%E2%80%99s%20ruling%2C%20the%20BJP%20executed%20a%20split%20in%20the%20Nationalist%20Congress%20Party%20%E2%80%93%20bringing%20Ajit%20Pawar%20and%20eight%20of%20his%20colleagues%20to%20join%20the%20Eknath%20Shinde%20cabinet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20initially%20bracketed%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20who%20are%20part%20of%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20INDIA%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgroup%20of%20corrupt%20leaders%E2%80%9D%20who%20are%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%2C%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20and%20Income%20Tax.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20BJP%20has%20far%20more%20corrupt%20leaders%20from%20east%20to%20west%20and%20from%20north%20to%20south.%20They%20were%20under%20the%20scanner%20of%20the%20central%20agencies%20for%20corruption.%20After%20joining%20the%20BJP%2C%20they%20stand%20cleaned%20in%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20washing%20machine%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20spokesman%2C%20Manoj%20Jha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20is%20said%20to%20be%20apprehensive%20because%20it%20had%20come%20to%20power%20in%202014%20after%20heaping%20charges%20of%20corruption%20and%20%E2%80%98policy%20paralysis%E2%80%99%20on%20the%20Manmohan%20Singh%20government.%20Now%2C%20the%20charges%20of%20incompetence%20and%20corruption%20against%20it%20%E2%80%93%20coupled%20with%20an%20organised%20opposition%20%E2%80%93%20can%20create%20a%20vicious%20anti-incumbency%20against%20the%20Modi%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EChemistry%20over%20arithmetic%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENitish%2C%20who%20is%20perceived%20as%20the%20de-facto%20convener%20of%20INDIA%2C%20said%20that%20the%20alliance%20will%20soon%20announce%20a%20policy%20for%20seat%20sharing.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20at%20work.%20But%20INDIA%20will%20work%20for%20the%20larger%20interest%20of%20the%20country%20and%20countrymen.%20They%20(BJP)%20are%20altering%20history%20and%20obliterating%20what%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20stood%20for.%20Does%20he%20(Modi)%20ever%20speak%20Bapu%E2%80%99s%20name%3F%20They%20(BJP)%20are%20annihilating%20our%20history%2C%20culture%20and%20values%E2%80%A6%20It%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20tolerated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bihar%20CM%20knows%20that%20just%20arithmetic%20is%20not%20enough%20to%20win%20seats%2C%20and%20even%20political%20chemistry%20is%20required.%20During%20the%202019%20general%20elections%2C%20Nitish%20and%20the%20JD(U)%20were%20with%20the%20NDA%20and%20swept%20Bihar%2C%20with%20all%20but%20one%20of%20the%2040%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party%20and%20the%20Bahujan%20Samaj%20Party%20(BSP)%20had%20the%20correct%20arithmetic%20when%20they%20entered%20into%20an%20alliance%20for%20the%202019%20polls.%20Had%20only%20the%20arithmetic%20determined%20the%20poll%20results%2C%20the%20BJP%20would%20have%20lost%2040-50%20seats%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20most%20populous%20state.%20But%20the%20saffron%20party%20won%2065%20seats.%20Observers%20say%20that%20the%20BJP%20had%20chemistry%20in%20its%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20the%20BSP%20is%20so%20far%20not%20the%20part%20of%20INDIA.%20But%20the%20INDIA%20leaders%20are%20not%20too%20concerned%20about%20it.%20With%20the%20Congress%20resurgent%20with%20its%20victory%20in%20Karnataka%20and%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20and%20Rahul%20Gandhi%E2%80%99s%20padyatra%2C%20Nitish%20and%20opposition%20strategists%20are%20believed%20to%20be%20working%20for%20chemistry%20over%20arithmetic.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETheir%20chemistry%20is%20visible%20in%20their%20floor%20coordination%20during%20the%20ongoing%20monsoon%20session%20of%20the%20parliament.%20It%E2%80%99s%20to%20be%20seen%20how%20they%20succeed%20at%20the%20level%20of%20the%20masses%20in%20the%20run%20up%20to%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENalin%20Verma%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%2C%20media%20educator%20and%20independent%20researcher%20in%20Folklore.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690464021000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13160506%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-4.04.26.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-narendra-modi-nervous%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Nitish%20Kumar%20said%20that%20the%20prime%20minister%20was%20%26quot%3Bscared%26quot%3B%20and%20therefore%C2%A0attempted%20to%20equate%20the%20alliance%20with%20the%20Indian%20Mujahideen%20and%20East%20India%20Company.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A26%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Findia-alliance-narendra-modi-nervous%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kuwait%20executes%205%20prisoners%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1690462816000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-102176257%2Cimgsize-128490.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fkuwait-executes-5-prisoners-including-a-man-convicted-in-2015-islamic-state-claimed-mosque-bombing%2Farticleshow%2F102175709.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F102175709.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EKuwait%20said%20on%20Thursday%20it%20executed%20five%20prisoners%2C%20including%20an%20inmate%20convicted%20over%20the%20bombing%20of