nt%20benefits%20fell%20by%207%2C000%20to%20221%2C000%20for%20the%20week%20ending%20July%2022%2C%20from%20228%2C000%20the%20week%20before%2C%20the%20Labor%20Department%20reported%20Thursday.%20That's%20the%20fewest%20since%20February.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fweekly-us-applications-for-jobless-benefits-slide-to-lowest-level-in-5-months%2Farticleshow%2F102176044.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fweekly-us-applications-for-jobless-benefits-slide-to-lowest-level-in-5-months%2Famp_articleshow%2F102176044.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fweekly-us-applications-for-jobless-benefits-slide-to-lowest-level-in-5-months%2Famp_articleshow%2F102176044.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Udupi%3A%20Despite%20Police's%20Denial%2C%20Hindutva%20Outfits%20Give%20Communal%20Spin%20to%20Row%20Over%20College%20Video%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F29120914%2FKarnataka-Police.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ENew%20Delhi%3C%2Fb%3E%3Cspan%3E%3A%20A%20recent%20incident%20in%20Karnataka%E2%80%99s%20communally%20sensitive%20Udupi%20has%20become%20yet%20another%20reminder%20of%20how%20the%20Hindutva%20right%20wing%20has%20mastered%20the%20use%20of%20social%20media%20to%20spread%20misinformation%2C%20communal%20hate%2C%20and%20sustain%20its%20rumour-mongering%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20July%2019%2C%20a%20case%20of%20alleged%20distasteful%20bullying%20in%20the%20Netra%20Jyothi%20College%2C%20a%20paramedical%20educational%20institution%20in%20Udupi%2C%20came%20to%20light.%20The%20college%20authorities%20received%20a%20complaint%20from%20a%20student%20that%20she%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fbengaluru-news%2Ffir-registered-against-students-and-management-in-bengaluru-for-restroom-video-incident-101690400368111.html%5C%22%3Efilmed%20secretly%20in%20a%20washroom%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20three%20fellow%20students%2C%20following%20which%20all%20three%20students%20were%20suspended.%20The%20complainant%20herself%20claimed%20that%20the%20three%20students%20were%20trying%20to%20pull%20a%20prank%20on%20one%20of%20their%20classmates%20but%20ended%20up%20videographing%20her.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20college%20management%20said%20that%20the%20suspended%20students%20apologised%20to%20the%20complainant%20and%20deleted%20the%20video%20immediately%20and%20that%20the%20complainant%20didn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20pursue%20a%20police%20case.%20The%20college%20put%20the%20matter%20to%20rest%20by%20suspending%20the%20three%20students%2C%20while%20also%20informing%20the%20local%20police%20of%20the%20matter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20within%20a%20day%2C%20the%20matter%20snowballed%20into%20a%20major%20controversy%20after%20several%20right-wing%20handles%20on%20social%20media%20communalised%20the%20matter%2C%20alleging%20that%20the%20three%20suspended%20students%2C%20who%20also%20happened%20to%20be%20Muslims%2C%20were%20apparently%20part%20of%20a%20%E2%80%9Cstatewide%20network%20to%20target%20Hindu%20women%E2%80%9D.%20The%20Karnataka%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%E2%80%99s%20(BJP%E2%80%99s)%20social%20media%20handles%20also%20alleged%20that%20the%20incident%20was%20a%20form%20of%20%E2%80%9Cjihad%E2%80%9D%20while%20giving%20a%20communal%20spin%20to%20the%20whole%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20several%20other%20social%20media%20handles%20also%20circulated%20an%20old%20video%20from%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20claiming%20that%20the%20recorded%20college%20video%20was%20being%20widely%20circulated%20on%20WhatsApp%20and%20other%20social%20media%20platforms.%20This%20was%20done%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20complainant%20had%20refused%20to%20file%20a%20police%20case.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOnce%20the%20matter%20became%20controversial%2C%20the%20Karnataka%20Police%2C%20after%20its%20initial%20investigation%2C%20categorically%20claimed%20that%20the%20matter%20was%20not%20a%20communal%20incident%20and%20that%20it%20would%20probe%20the%20alleged%20fake%20propaganda%20around%20the%20incident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20right-wing%20activists%20went%20on%20overdrive%20when%20the%20police%20tried%20to%20question%20one%20Rashmi%20Samant%2C%20whose%20tweet%20alleged%20that%20the%20college%20incident%20was%20part%20of%20an%20%E2%80%9CIslamist%20conspiracy%E2%80%9D%20and%20that%20videos%20of%20the%20incident%20were%20being%20circulated%20had%20gone%20viral.%20Although%20the%20police%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20probe%20her%2C%20because%20she%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20at%20her%20home%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20police%20visit%2C%20several%20right-wing%20activists%20were%20affronted%20by%20the%20fact%20that%20Samant%20was%20questioned.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUdupi%E2%80%99s%20BJP%20MLA%20Yashpal%20Suvarna%20landed%20at%20Samant%E2%80%99s%20residence%20in%20solidarity.%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Karnataka%20state%20unit%20president%20Naleen%20Kumar%20Kateel%20and%20BJP%20IT%20cell%20head%20Amit%20Malviya%2C%20came%20to%20Samant%E2%80%99s%20defence%2C%20while%20also%20accusing%20the%20Congress%20government%20in%20the%20state%20of%20acting%20in%20a%20partisan%20manner%20and%20leading%20a%20social%20media%20campaign%20containing%20misinformation%2C%20exaggerations%2C%20and%20communal%20remarks%20against%20the%20suspended%20students%20and%20the%20Muslim%20community%20in%20general.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%E2%80%99m%20from%20Udupi%20and%20nobody%20is%20talking%20about%20Alimatul%20Shaifa%2C%20Shabanaz%20and%20