2C%20of%20serving%20Maa%20Bharati%2C%20and%20dreaming%20of%20New%20India.%20These%20dreams%20are%20largely%20linked%20to%20the%20goal%20of%20%245%20trillion%20economy%2C%E2%80%9D%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fpm-modi-varanasi-5-trillion-economy-budget-1563362-2019-07-06%5C%22%3EModi%20had%20said%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20in%20mid-June%2C%202023%2C%20Union%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%E2%80%99s%20office%20tweeted%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20had%20touched%20the%20%243.75%20trillion%20mark%20in%202023.%20This%20would%20mean%20that%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20%245-trillion%20figure%20is%20still%20a%20long%20way%20off%20and%20quite%20difficult%20considering%20the%202024-25%20deadline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESitharaman%20is%20not%20the%20only%20government%20figure%20who%20has%20spoken%20of%20trillion%20figures%20that%20fall%20short%20of%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20initial%20%E2%80%98%245-trillion%20economy%E2%80%99%20claim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Sitharaman%E2%80%99s%20tweet%20mentioned%20%243.75%20trillion%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20chief%20economic%20advisor%20V.%20Anantha%20Nageswaran%20had%20earlier%20in%20the%20year%20said%20that%20the%20Indian%20economy%20will%20be%20a%20%E2%80%9C%243%20trillion%20one%20at%20current%20prices%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%202022-23%20fiscal%20year%E2%80%9D.%20Nageswaran%20also%20said%20that%20it%20is%20expected%20to%20touch%20the%20%247-trillion%20mark%20%E2%80%9Cin%20the%20next%20seven%20years.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Ffive-trillion-dollar-economy-india%5C%22%3EAs%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20reported%20earlier%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Bibek%20Debroy%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Economic%20Advisory%20Council%20to%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Findias-gdp-nearing-to-20-trillion-says-bibek-debroy-11672851470248.html%5C%22%3Eh