E%3Cstrong%3EOther%20promises%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%245-trillion%20dollar%20economy%20promise%20is%20not%20the%20only%20one%20that%20Modi%20has%20unveiled.%20From%20time%20to%20time%2C%20he%20has%20made%20others%20in%20the%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.livemint.com%2FPolitics%2FZ4EoA2KOVT07UGcOt8MglI%2FManipur-elections-2017-Narendra-Modi-promises-to-end-econom.html%5C%22%3Epromised%20to%20end%3C%2Fa%3E%20what%20had%20then%20proven%20to%20be%20a%20crippling%20economic%20blockade%20launched%20by%20United%20Naga%20Council%20in%20Manipur%20if%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20state%20the%20assembly%20election%2C%20which%20it%20did.%20The%20blockade%20was%20also%20lifted%20in%20March.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202016%2C%20Modi%20had%20promised%20to%20double%20farmers%E2%80%99%20income%20by%202022%2C%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Bareilly%20of%20Uttar%20Pradesh.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnarendra-modi-governance-myth-reality%5C%22%3ETalk%20of%20this%20has%20died%20down%20now.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrior%20to%20election%20in%202014%2C%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20had%20promised%20that%20each%20person%E2%80%99s%20bank%20account%20would%20be%20credited%20with%20Rs%2015%20lakh%20if%20they%20came%20to%20power.%20This%20did%20not%20come%20to%20pass%2C%20with%20a%20Ranchi%20court%20even%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Fpm-narendra-modi-amit-shah-case-ranchi-court-election-promise-1642942-2020-02-03%5C%22%3Eopening%3C%2Fa%3E%20proceedings%20by%20a%20petitioner%20who%20held%20them%20culpable%20for%20reneging%20on%20this%20promise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20stressing%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20resolve%20to%20bring%20food%20prices%20under%20check%2C%20Modi%2C%20in%202014%2C%20had%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CNo%20person%20should%20go%20to%20bed%20hungry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20promised%20to%20control%20inflation.%20We%20are%20determined%20achieve%20this%20target%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20do%20this%20(control%20inflation)%20not%20only%20because%20it%20is%20our%20election%20promise%20but%20we%20want%20every%20poor%20to%20have%20access%20to%20food%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20during%20his%20term%2C%20India%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fnews%2F2022%2F10%2F15%2Findia-hunger%5C%22%3Efared%20worse%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20other%20South%20Asian%20countries%20such%20as%20Pakistan%2C%20Nepal%2C%20Bangladesh%20and%20Sri%20Lanka%20in%20the%20global%20hunger%20index.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnemployment%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Farticle%2Feconomy-policy%2Funemployment-rate-at-five-decade-high-of-6-1-in-2017-18-nsso-survey-119013100053_1.html%5C%22%3Eclimbed%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20a%2045-year%20high%20in%202017-18.%20It%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20got%20any%20better%20since.%20Mahesh%20Vyas%2C%20chief%20of%20Centre%20for%20Monitoring%20Indian%20Economy%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Findias-workforce-not-rising-quality-of-jobs-very-low-cmies-mahesh-vyas%5C%22%3Ehad%20told%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20workforce%20%E2%80%93%20which%20is%20usually%20understood%20as%20the%20set%20of%20people%20who%20are%20employed%20%E2%80%93%20is%20not%20rising.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20quality%20of%20jobs%20in%20India%20is%20very%20low.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20Modi%20government%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmintgenie.livemint.com%2Fnews%2Fmarkets%2Finfra-sector-the-keystone-to-india-s-5-trillion-dollar-economy-goal-151669270018214%5C%22%3E%20is%20betting%20on%20infrastructure%20creation%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20reach%20the%20trillion%20dollar%20target%2C%20many%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.statista.com%2Fstatistics%2F1083540%2Findia-access-to-toilets-by-type%2F%5C%22%