Fa%3E%C2%A0in%20relation%20to%20the%20leak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20data%20leak%20%E2%80%93%20including%20names%2C%20Aadhaar%20national%20IDs%2C%20mobile%20numbers%2C%20voter%20IDs%2C%20passports%20and%20COVID%20vaccination%20status%20of%20millions%20of%20individuals%20%E2%80%93%20was%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20in%20India%2C%20and%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20other%20breaches%20of%20CoWIN%20and%20Aadhaar%20data%2C%20and%20the%20records%20of%20a%20leading%20hospital%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20recent%20breaches%20of%20health%20data%20are%20particularly%20concerning%2C%20digital%20experts%20said%2C%20as%20they%20leave%20individuals%20vulnerable%20to%20scams%2C%20harassment%20and%20discrimination%20without%20remedy%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20a%20data%20protection%20law%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20warned%20it%20also%20undermines%20India%E2%80%99s%20aim%20to%20develop%20and%20export%20to%20Asian%20and%20African%20countries%20its%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20model%20comprising%20Aadhaar%2C%20mobile%20payment%20system%20UPI%20and%20the%20National%20Health%20Stack%20data%20platform%2C%20that%20authorities%20say%20will%20improve%20access%20and%20efficiency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%20pushing%20its%20digital%20public%20infrastructure%20%E2%80%9CIndia%20is%20putting%20people%20at%20risk%20from%20data%20collection%20and%20data%20overreach%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Raman%20Jit%20Singh%20Chima%2C%20Asia%20policy%20director%20at%20digital%20rights%20group%20Access%20Now.%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20a%20bad%20model.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20push%20for%20greater%20digitisation%20of%20health%20data%20is%20happening%20without%20discussion%20or%20adequate%20data%20protection.%20India%20is%20seeing%20an%20increase%20in%20cyberattacks%2C%20and%20the%20refusal%20to%20acknowledge%20breaches%20and%20to%20hold%20institutions%20accountable%20is%20a%20reckless%20approach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20minist