id%20Aarushi%20Gupta%20at%20Digital%20Futures%20Lab%2C%20a%20research%20collective.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20the%20vast%20amounts%20of%20data%20collection%2C%20processing%2C%20and%20exchange%20%E2%80%A6%20citizens%20are%20at%20considerable%20risk%20of%20their%20data%20being%20leaked%20and%20their%20privacy%20rights%20being%20compromised%2C%20as%20seen%20with%20the%20recent%20leak%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20was%20the%20biggest%20target%20for%20cyberattacks%20after%20the%20United%20States%20in%202021%20and%202022%2C%20with%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cloudsek.com%2Fthreatintelligence%2Fcowin-data-leak-claim-and-cloudsek-analysis%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enearly%20500%20attacks%20last%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20increase%20of%20nearly%20a%20fourth%2C%20according%20to%20cybersecurity%20firm%20CloudSEK.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20separate%20study%20by%20NordVPN%2C%20a%20virtual%20private%20network%20service%20provider%2C%20last%20year%20showed%20India%20was%20the%20worst%20hit%20by%20data%20breaches%2C%20with%20some%C2%A0%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Ftechnology%2Fstolen-data-600000-indians-sold-bot-markets-so-far-study-2022-12-08%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E600%2C000%20people%20having%20had%20their%20data%20stolen%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0and%20sold%20on%20bot%20markets%20by%20hackers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27162824%2Fdata-hacks-Indiaresize.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F27162824%2Fdata-hacks-Indiaresize.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewir