ent.%20The%20blame%20is%20put%20on%20the%20children%20%E2%80%94%20not%20just%20those%20with%20disabilities%2C%20but%20also%20those%20who%20have%20a%20different%20way%20of%20learning.%20We%20label%20them%20as%20%E2%80%98naughty%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98lazy%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%98not%20interested%E2%80%99%E2%80%A6The%20system%20is%20designed%20in%20a%20way%20to%20exclude%20at%20multiple%20levels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%E2%80%99s%20a%20very%20academic%2C%20literal%20way%20of%20learning%2C%20when%20the%20fact%20is%20that%20children%20universally%20learn%20better%20by%20doing.%20This%20idea%20is%20not%20even%20well%20understood%2C%20let%20alone%20implemented.%20If%20we%20cater%20to%20this%20difference%20in%20ways%20of%20learning%2C%20we%20will%20automatically%20move%20towards%20more%20inclusivity.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERupa%20emphasises%20on%20a%20social-emotional%20learning%20(SEL)%20curriculum.%20This%20is%20a%20process%20by%20which%20a%20child%20learns%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F285570%2Fchild-sexual-abuse-survivor-circles-of-safety-sexuality-education-school-curriculum%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunderstand%2C%20express%2C%20and%20manage%20emotions%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20focused%20on%20helping%20them%20build%20healthy%20relationships%2C%20manage%20positive%20and%20negative%20feelings%2C%20and%20develop%20a%20sense%20of%20empathy%20and%20right%20or%20wrong.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20need%20to%20make%20each%20child%20feel%20significant%2C%20and%20have%20a%20sense%20of%20belonging%20in%20the%20classroom.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrQjc7lORj2%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FCrQjc7lORj2%2