0cost%20that%20went%20into%20building%20these%20playgrounds.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEducation%20should%20never%20be%20about%20textbook-based%20learning%20alone.%20The%20focus%20should%20be%20on%20the%20holistic%20development%20of%20children.%20Play%20is%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20the%20overall%20growth%20of%20a%20child.%20We%20have%20been%20mandated%20to%20focus%20on%20early%20childhood%20development%20(ECD)%20by%20the%20Union%20and%20State%20government%20because%20this%20is%20the%20time%20when%20children%20learn%20the%20most%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Innovate%20playgrounds%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152.jpg%201080w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FSnapinsta.app_171386959_474560363748134_6669212032293108365_n_1080-1689947152-150x78.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324803%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22565%5C%22%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20can%20be%20done%20to%20improve%20playground%20infrastructure%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20said%20that%2C%20in%20rural%20areas%20and%20in%20more%20remote%20geographies%2C%20Rai%20argues%20that%20we%20need%20more%20playgrounds.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20built%20playgrounds%20in%2023%20states%2C%20but%20not%20one%20in%20Bihar%20or%20Chhattisgarh%20for%20a%20variety%20of%20reasons.%20There%20is%20a%20big%20need%20for%20playgrounds%20in%20those%20states%2C%20but%20we%E2%80%99ve%20just%20not%20been%20able%20to%20raise%20funding%20to%20build%20playgrounds%20in%20those%20states.%20So%2C%20I%20think%20there%E2%80%99s%20an%20imbalance%20in%20where%20these%20playground%20resources%20are%20available%20and%20where%20the%20need%20is%20most%20urgent%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20do%20you%20resolve%20this%20conundrum%3F%20Rai%20notes%20that%20one%20of%20the%20biggest%20things%20that%20can%20be%20done%20is%20bringing%20the%20government%2C%20corporates%20and%20playground%20builders%20together.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20lot%20of%20times%20we%20see%20there%20is%20funding%2C%20but%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20government%20support.%20At%20other%20places%2C%20we%20have%20government%20support%2C%20but%20do%20not%20have%20funds.%20Bringing%20all%20three%20parties%20together%20has%20been%20a%20challenge.%20There%20are%20occasions%20when%20the%20government%20has%20funding%2C%20and%20they%20just%20install%20a%20few%20plastic%20slides%2C%20which%20is%20okay%20but%20not%20good%20enough.%20They%20can%20bring%20in%20organisations%20like%20us%20who%20are%20building%20playgrounds%20at%20lower%20cost%20that%20are%20also%20more%20durable%20and%20help%20in%20children%E2%80%99s%20growth%20and%20learning.%20We%20must%20align%20different%20stakeholders%20to%20one%20common%20mission%2C%E2%80%9D%20claims%20Rai.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAccording%20to%20the%20All%20India%20School%20Education%20Survey%20conducted%20in%202016%2C%2062%25%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20h