re%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20teaches%20them%20how%20to%20cook%20%3Cem%3Edal%20%3C%2Fem%3E(lentil%20gravy)%2C%20%3Cem%3Ealu%20gobi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(potato%20cauliflower%20stir%20fry)%2C%20paneer%20butter%20%3Cem%3Emasala%20%3C%2Fem%3E(gravy%20cooked%20with%20cottage%20cheese)%2C%20%3Cem%3Echapati%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Egatte%20ki%20sabji%20%3C%2Fem%3E(a%20traditional%20Rajasthani%20curry%20made%20with%20chickpea%20flour%20sausages)%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Enaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20(flatbread).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%20cooks%20a%20unique%20kind%20of%20garlic%20cheese%20made%20from%20hung%20curd%2C%20pepper%2C%20and%20chopped%20garlic%20which%20is%20applied%20over%20hot%20%3Cem%3Enaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20or%20%3Cem%3Echapati%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20served%20with%20tomato%20curry.%20%E2%80%9COur%20guests%20love%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says%20with%20pride.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20five-hour%20class%2C%20which%20is%20priced%20at%20INR%201%2C500%20per%20person%2C%20the%20guests%20relish%20the%20cooked%20meals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDaniel%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20learning%20experience%20is%20great%20mainly%20because%20the%20classes%20are%20organised%20at%20Shashi%E2%80%99s%20home.%20She%20tells%20you%20her%20life%20story%20also%20which%20helps%20us%20engage%20with%20her.%20Both%2C%20Shashi%20and%20her%20son%2C%20who%20helps%20her%20in%20cooking%2C%20are%20very%20didactic%3B%20not%20only%20in%20following%20recipes%2C%20but%20also%20in%20teaching%20the%20basics%20of%20Indian%20cuisine.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20love%20cooking%20and%20I%E2%80%99m%20excited%20to%20use%20everything%20I%20learned%20from%20Shashi%E2%80%99s%20class%20in%20Spain.%20I%E2%80%99ll%20definitely%20put%20those%20skills%20into%20practice%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20840px)%20100vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22After%20a%20five-hour%20class%2C%20the%20guests%20relish%20the%20cooked%20meals.%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22840%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-2-1689859229-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324597%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22439%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAfter%20a%20five-hour%20class%2C%20the%20guests%20relish%20the%20cooked%20meals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShashi%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20focus%20is%20not%20to%20only%20earn%20an%20income%20from%20these%20guests%20but%20also%20to%20treat%20them%20nicely%20because%20they%20are%20our%20guests.%20They%20should%20be%20happy%20when%20they%20go%20back%20to%20their%20homes.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20even%20pay%20me%20extra%20on%20their%20own%20out%20of%20love.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOther%20than%20delectable%20meals%2C%20these%20tourists%20also%20enjoy%20Shashi%E2%80%99s%20company%2C%20who%20does%20not%20miss%20a%20chance%20to%20entertain%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20apply%20henna%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eon%20their%20palms%20and%20help%20our%20women%20guests%20wear%20a%20saree%20with%20bangles%20and%20bindi.%20I%20also%20apply%20%3Cem%3Esindoor%20%3C%2Fem%3E(vermillion)%20to%20them.%20They%20are%20enthusiastic%20to%20participate%20in%20all%20these%20activities%20and%20show%20a%20keen%20interest%20in%20knowing%20the%20Indian%20culture.%20They%20often%20request%20me%20to%20narrate%20stories%20of%20gods%20and%20goddesses%2C%20explain%20the%20significance%20of%20%3Cem%3Etulsi%20%3C%2Fem%3E(basil)%20plant%2C%20etc%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20celebrate%20their%20birthdays.%20In%20their%20own%20dialects%2C%20they%20lovingly%20call%20me%20%E2%80%98aunty%E2%80%99%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds%20with%20a%20smile.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Shashi%2C%20teaching%20these%20foreign%20tourists%20helps%20her%20feel%20empowered.%20%E2%80%9CI%20always%20believed%20in%20hard%20work.%20No%20one%20can%20defeat%20you%20if%20you%20believe%20in%20yourself.%20%3Cem%3ERoya%20daan%20nai%20milta%2C%20aur%20maangi%20bheek%20%3C%2Fem%3E(You%20won%E2%80%99t%20always%20get%20alms%20by%20crying).%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3EI%20have%20learnt%20that%20there%20is%20no%20point%20in%20crying%20in%20front%20of%20others%2C%20empower%20yourself%20to%20go%20on%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689946319000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2Fshashi-cooking-classes-3-1689859353.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D324582%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20losing%20her%20husband%2C%20Shashikala%20Sanadhya%20took%20care%20of%20her%20family%20by%20starting%20Shashi%20Cooking%20Classes.%20So%20far%2C%20she%20has%20taught%20over%201%2C000%20foreign%20tourists%20how%20to%20cook%20homely%20Indian%20food%20like%20chapati%2C%20naan%2C%20pakora%2C%20chutney%20and%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A297%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F324582%2Fshashikala-sanadhya-gives-indian-food-cooking-lessons-for-foreign-tourists-in-udaipur%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Play%2C%20Learn%2C%20Grow%2C%20Repeat%3A%20A%20Peak%20Inside%20India%E2%80%99s%20Innovative%2C%20DIY%2C%20Sustainable%20Playgrounds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20was%20published%20in%20collaboration%20with%20EkStep%20Foundation.%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Pooja%20Rai%20was%20a%20student%20of%20architecture%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F275217%2Fiit-kharagpur-innovation-oral-cancer-screening-cheap-device%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIndian%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20(IIT)%2C%20Kharagpur%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20would%20volunteer%20at%20Disha%20Seema%20Care%20Centre%2C%20a%20school%20for%20underprivileged%20children%20located%20on%20campus.%20During%20one%20visit%2C%20she%20observed%20a%20few%20girls%20playing%20on%20broken%20cement%20pipes%20while%20some%20construction%20work%20was%20going%20on%20nearby.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20extremely%20unsafe%20because%20you%20had%20wires%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20pipes%20and%20there%20were%20broken%20pieces%20of%20cement%20lying%20around.%20I%20also%20saw%20some%20boys%20at%20school%20trying%20to%20play%20a%20game%20of%20badminton%20with%20their%20slippers.%20Even%20though%20there%20was%20so%20much%20joy%20in%20that%20space%2C%20it%20just%20made%20me%20think%20that%20these%20children%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20have%20access%20to%20something%20as%20simple%20as%20a%20playground.%20Talking%20to%20my%20friend%20that%20evening%2C%20we%20discussed%20how%20we%20could%20use%20all%20the%20design%20knowledge%20that%20we%20learned%20to%20build%20a%20playground%20for%20these%20kids%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rai%2C%20speaking%20to%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20Pooja%20and%20her%20batchmates%20were%20students%2C%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20money.%20Instead%20of%20building%20a%20conventional%20playground%20with%20a%20jungle%20gym%2C%20merry%20go%20round%20and%20slides%2C%20they%20got%20innovative%2C%20brought%20a%20few%20tires%20together%2C%20and%20built%20a%20different%20kind%20of%20playground.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201193px)%20100vw%2C%201193px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221193%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Playgrounds%20for%20children%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320.jpg%201193w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320-300x183.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320-500x306.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320-768x469.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FAnthill-Playgrounds-8-1689854320-150x92.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-324513%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22729%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EPlayground%20at%20the%20Disha%20Seema%20Care%20Centre.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20%E2%80%98DIY%E2%80%99%20playground%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CInitially%2C%20we%20struggled%20to%20collect%20tires%2C%20but%20we%20got%20lucky%20after%20reaching%20out%20to%20a%20few%20companies.%20Michelin%2C%20a%20global%20tyre%20manufacturer%2C%20sponsored%20the%20very%20first%20playground%20we%20built.%20They%20sent%20us%20used%20tires%2C%20with%20which%20we%20built%20swings%20and%20other%20play%20elements%20for%20children.%20They%20also%20sponsored%20a%20part%20of%20the%20project%2C%20while%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20funding%20came%20from%20our%20college%20alumni.%20We%20built%20our%20first%20playground%20in%202015%20and%20it%20was%20completely%20DIY%20(%E2%80%98do%20it%20yourself%E2%80%99)%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20recalls.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20Rai%20and%20her%20batchmates%20built%20here%20was%20a%20low-cost%20(barely%20Rs%2020%2C000)%20and%20sustainable%20playground%20for%20underprivileged%20children.%20According%20to%20Rai%2C%20mass%20produced%20recreational%20equipment%20for%20building%20a%20playground%20at%20the%20time%20would%20typically%20cost%20about%20Rs%202%20lakh.%20What%20followed%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20media%20coverage%20and%20inquiries%20from%20all%20around%20the%20country%20to%20build%20similar%20structures.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%20January%202017%2C%20Rai%20and%20her%20friends%20quit%20their%20jobs%20full%20time%20and%20established%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20non-profit%20called%20Anthill%20Creations%2C%20which%20%E2%80%9Ctransforms%20spaces%20into%20interactive%20and%20sustainable%20playgrounds%20by%20upcycling%20waste%20materials%20like%20tyres%2C%20oil%20and%20cable%20drums.%E2%80%9D%20So%20far%2C%20they%20have%20built%20around%20380%20low-cost%20and%20sustainable%20playgrounds%20for%20children%20across%2022%20states%20including%20Karnataka%2C%20Maharashtra%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Odisha%2C%20Meghalaya%2C%20Tripura%2C%20amongst%20others.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20are%20playgrounds%20important%20for%20children%20in%20the%20first%20place%3F%20Educationists%20note%20that%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Fchildhooddialogues%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearly%20childhood%20care%20and%20education%20(ECCE)%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20play-based%20learning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Ftv%2FCZjg3gapFqJ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloadi